>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:none; border-left:none; border-right:none; border-top:none; width:113px\"> </td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:none; border-left:none; border-right:none; border-top:none; width:10px\"> </td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:none; border-left:none; border-right:none; border-top:none; width:103px\"> </td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:none; border-left:none; border-right:none; border-top:none; width:14px\"> </td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:none; border-left:none; border-right:none; border-top:none; width:108px\"> </td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:none; border-left:none; border-right:none; border-top:none; width:144px\"> </td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:none; border-left:none; border-right:none; border-top:none; width:123px\"> </td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">AKASH Standard Package (6 or 12 -month EMI)</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Avail EMI for 6 months on online purchase of AKASH connection. For a total price of BDT 5,640 you only have to pay a monthly installment of BDT 940. Free installation subject to terms and conditions of refund policy provided in akashdth.com.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Avail EMI for 12 months on online purchase of AKASH connection. For a total price of BDT 5,880 you only have to pay a monthly installment of BDT 490. Free installation subject to terms and conditions of refund policy provided in akashdth.com.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">AKASH Standard Package plus subscription (6- or 12-month EMI</span></strong><strong>)</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Avail EMI for 6 months on online purchase of AKASH connection. For a total price of BDT 8070 inclusive of 6-months’ subscription you only have to pay a monthly installment of BDT 1345. 1-month Subscription and Installation free subject to terms and conditions of refund policy provided in akashdth.com.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Avail EMI for 12 months on online purchase of AKASH connection. For a total price of BDT 11,160 inclusive of 12-months’ subscription you only have to pay a monthly installment of BDT 930. 2-month Subscription and Installation free subject to terms and conditions of refund policy provided in akashdth.com.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\">Things to note:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Applicable for selected cards of selected banks only.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Interest applicable on EMI, interest rates are variable depending on the tenure of EMI.  </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">Product will be delivered within 2 working days and installation completed within 3 working days in Dhaka, Chittagong and Sylhet metro.</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">Beyond metro areas, product delivery and installation will be completed within 3 working days.</span></p>\n', '1570043295-86032692.jpg', '1570044221-68539046.jpg', '', 'EMI', 0, 0, 1, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2020-06-28 01:14:41', '201