sup>nd</sup> December 2019 to 17th January 2020 otherwise you won\'t be eligible.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I\'m a current subscriber of AKASH. Am I eligible to participate?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> No, only subscribers purchasing the full connection or the STB from 22nd December to 17th January are eligible to participate. If you have purchased AKASH before December 22nd 2019, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional connections or STBs during 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020!</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Do I need to recharge after activating my connection to participate in this campaign?  </span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> No you don\'t need to recharge. Existing or new customers purchasing the full connection or the STB from 22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020 and activating during this specified campaign period are eligible to participate.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">I bought AKASH Connection/STB before 22nd December 2019 but my installation has been completed on or after 22nd December 2019; am I eligible for the campaign?</sp