ily:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">Yes, only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber </span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">What do I need to bring to collect prizes?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> The winner needs to show the Winner confirmation SMS from AKASH and have valid identity card and proof of ownership of the registered number in order to collect the entitled prize. Details will be communicated to the winners at the time we call the winners.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Will I get SMS/any notification if I don\'t win any prizes?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> No, only the winners will be notified.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Will the winners get any transportation allowance for visiting the designated point to collect the prizes?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans: </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">No transportation allowance would be provided to winners when collecting the prize</span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Can I get the equivalent cash amount for the prize won?</span></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Ans:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> Prizes won are not transferable and cannot be combined with any other prize or any other offer or discounts or promotions offered by AKASH. Only in the events of exhaustion of existing stock or due to political instability, natural calamities, in such cases prizes will be replaced by other available prizes of same monetary value</span></span></span></p>\n', '1577021050-37562047.jpg', '1577021050-75021253.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 1, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2020-02-01 11:02:41', '2019-12-22 19:24:10', '', 140),
(6, 'BPL Campaign with Daraz', 'bpl-campaign-with-daraz', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> 22<sup>nd</sup> December – 17<sup>th</sup> January, 2020 </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Participant Eligibility and Modality: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone buying AKASH DTH from Daraz platform and activating within the campaign period (22<sup>nd</sup> December to 17<sup>th</sup> January, 2020) are eligible for the campaign.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Other than guaranteed 1-month free subscription, purchasers of AKASH DTH connection from Daraz will also get chance to win exclusive cricket ball signed by the BPL team captains through a lucky draw (After the end of the campaign).</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Winner Announcement:</strong> Through SMS and Facebook page of AKASH DTH (After end of the campaign)</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Available Prizes other than Confirm 1-Month Free Subscription:</u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">BPL Captain’s Signed Ball (Only)</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">​<strong><u>TERMS & CONDITIONS</u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH BPL Daraz Campaign will remain active from 22<sup>nd</sup> December – 17<sup>th</sup> January, 2020. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The purchaser must be Bangladeshi (Nationality) to be eligible for the campaign. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone purchasing full AKASH connection (CPE) or only the STB from Daraz, and activating during the campaign period are eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Other terms and conditions set by daraz for purchase of products through their platform will be applicable</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Existing AKASH DTH subscribers or inactive customer are not eligible to participate in the campaign, however they can participate through purchase of new AKASH connection during the campaign period (22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020)</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Prizes will be distributed after the end of the campaign, AKASH team will inform the winners regarding the prize distribution date and prize collection process.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">People purchasing product before 22nd December 2019, but activating during the campaign period (22nd December 2019 to 17th January 2020) are not be eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) and Daraz reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">No travel allowance will be provided to the winners, for collecting their prizes from AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.)</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '1577083617-39049529.jpg', '1577083617-87091580.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 1, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2020-02-02 10:36:51', '2019-12-23 12:46:57', '', 139);
