(7, 'Cash Back Campaign', 'cash-back-campaign', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\">Campaign Timeline</span></u></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\">: </span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\">1-31 January, 2020</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\">Participant Eligibility and Modality</span></u></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\">:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\">Anyone buying AKASH DTH activating and recharging within the campaign period (1<sup>st</sup> January to 31<sup>st</sup> January, 2020) are eligible for the AKASH UTSHOB CASHBACK campaign.</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-right:26px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\">All eligible participants are entitled to guaranteed cashback from BDT 100 up to BDT 100,000 by participating in the weekly campaign quiz.</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\"> The cashback of BDT 100 and 5000 would be recharged in the subscribers AKASH account and cashback of BDT 10K, 20K, 100K would be handed over to the winner in person. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">All new subscribers who have bought, activated and recharged a minimum of BDT 399 for AKASH during this campaign period will have to correctly answer a question of the campaign quiz which is to be conducted via an automated Interactive Voice Response (IVR) and the top winners to correctly answer in the shortest possible time will be selected as the winner on the basis of fastest finger first. On a weekly basis (i.e. 2<sup>nd</sup>,3<sup>rd</sup> and 4<sup>th</sup> week of January 2020), AKASH will announce the winners out of eligible participants who will successfully finish the campaign quiz modality as described below. The winner and participant of a single week are not eligible to participate in the campaign quiz for the next and the upcoming weeks for the month of January, for one particular connection but if customer buys another connection within the campaign period, he/she would be eligible to participate in the upcoming week. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-right:26px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\">Campaign Quiz Modality: </span></u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong>An SMS would be sent on 9th,16th, 22nd and 29th of January 2020, to all eligible participants who would have to give a missed call from their registered AKASH cell number to 09612200800 and against their missed call the participant will get an automatic computer-generated call through which the participant will be required to answer one (1) question and the winner would be selected on the basis of “Fastest Finger First” method.  Participants would be allowed a maximum of 24 hours to participate from the time participant receives the quiz eligibility confirmation SMS. For details call 16442.</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\">Winner Announcement:</span></span></u></strong><strong> </strong>Through phone call, SMS and Facebook page of AKASH DTH (Weekly 10th, 17th, 23rd, 30th January). Top 3 winners will get a phone call and others will get an SMS. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\">Available Prizes:</span></u></strong> </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Cashback of BDT 100,000,20,000,10,000, 5000 for 1 person respectively per week and BDT 100 for the other winners of the quiz. </span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\"\">TERMS & CONDITIONS</span></u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Anyone purchasing full AKASH connection (CPE) or only the STB from authorized Retail outlets and online (Incl. through EMI, FnF Package and Corporate Offer) within Bangladesh, and activating during the campaign period are eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Retailer/Distributor of AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) are not eligible to participate.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Employees of AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.), their parents, siblings, spouses & children are not eligible to participate.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Cashback of BDT 100,000, 20,000, 10,000, 5,000 and 100 to top winners will be distributed on a weekly basis, AKASH team will inform the winners regarding the prize distribution date and cashback collection process or BDT 100,000, 20,000,10,000 and for cashback of 100 and 5,000 it would be recharged in subscriber’s AKASH wallet.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">People purchasing product before 1<sup>st</sup> January 2020, but activating during the campaign period (1– 31 January, 2020) are not be eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) assures its customers/subscribers that, there is no financial investment, deposit, security money required to enter AKASH CASHBACK Campaign, all the customers/subscribers are requested to remain cautious for any such type of fraudulent offer.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; margin-right:84px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><em>(Beximco Communications Ltd. won’t be responsible for any kind of personal or financial loss due to any fraudulent incident)</em></span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">No transportation allowance would be provided to winners when collecting the prize.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">By participating, the subscriber/ purchaser agrees to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. Subscriber /purchaser must comply with these Terms & Conditions to be able to receive prize at the end of this campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) shall not be liable for any loss, damage or injury suffered or sustained (even if caused by negligence) as a result of accepting and/or using the prize, except for any liability which cannot be excluded by law.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-right:84px; text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-right:84px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-size:20.0pt\">Frequently Asked Questions</span></span></span></p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; width:100.0%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#aeaaaa; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong>SL</strong></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#aeaaaa; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; width:35%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong>Question</strong></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#aeaaaa; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; width:57%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong>Answer</strong></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">1</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">What is AKASH UTSHOB: CASHBACK Campaign?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">AKASH always strives to make the magical AKASH experience the most rewarding experience for you! AKASH has more than 40 HD channels and 120 total channels. Soon there will be even more! </span></span></p>\n\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Anyone buying AKASH DTH from our authorized retail outlets, direct sales, Daraz, Referral campaign, EMI and online within Bangladesh, activating and recharging within the campaign period (1st January to 31st January, 2020) are eligible for the AKASH UTSHOB CASHBACK campaign.</span></span></p>\n\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">All eligible participants are entitled to guaranteed cash back from BDT 100 up to BDT 100,000 by participating in the campaign quiz. The prize money of BDT 100 and 5,000 would be recharged in the subscribers AKASH wallet and prize money of BDT 10,000, 20,000, 100,000 would be handed over to the winner in person.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">2</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">How long is the duration of this campaign?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">The campaign will run from 1-31 January, 2020. You have to purchase an AKASH Connection, activate & Recharge minimum BDT 399 within the time frame to participate in weekly campaign quiz.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">3</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">If I purchase only STB, will I be eligible to participate?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Yes! If you purchase the full AKASH connection or only the STB, activate & recharge minimum BDT 399 you\'ll be eligible to participate in the campaign quiz! You\'ll have to buy the STB or the full connection from 1-31 January, 2020 otherwise you won\'t be eligible.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">4</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">I\'m a current subscriber of AKASH. Am I eligible to participate?</span></span></p>\n\n			<p> </p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">No, only subscribers purchasing the full connection or the STB from 1-31 January are eligible to participate. If you have purchased AKASH before 1st January 2020, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional connections or STBs during 1-31 January 2020 and participating in the campaign quiz.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">5</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Do I need to recharge after activating my connection to participate in this campaign?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Yes, you need to recharge. After purchasing the full connection or the STB, you need to activate and recharge minimum BDT 399 between 1-31 January 2020 to become eligible to participate in campaign quiz.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">6</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">I bought AKASH Connection/STB before 1st January 2020 but my installation has been completed on or after 1st January 2020; am I eligible for the campaign?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">No, only subscribers purchasing, activating and recharging the full connection or the STB from 1-31 January 2020 are eligible to participate in campaign quiz. If you have purchased AKASH before 1st January 2020, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional connections or STBs during 1-31 January 2020!</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">7</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">I\'m an employee of AKASH/Beximco</span></span></p>\n\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Communications Limited. Will I be eligible to participate?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Employees of Beximco Communications Limited, their parents, siblings, spouses & children are not eligible to participate.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">8</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">I’m an employee of Beximco Group. Am I eligible?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Yes, you are!</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"> </p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">I’m a new subscriber of AKASH; I got one month free subscription through referral program/other programs/special offer. Do I need to recharge to participate in the quiz?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Yes, you’ll have to recharge BDT 399 minimum. But don’t worry! Your free subscription will be valid as well! </span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">9</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">If I purchase through EMI or Online within 1-31 January 2020, will I be eligible?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Yes! You will be eligible if you purchase, activate and recharge full AKASH connection or STB through EMI, Online, Daraz or any authorized retail points within 1-31 January 2020.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">9</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">I am a retailer/Distributor of AKASH. Am I eligible for this contest/How can I participate in this contest?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">No, you cannot participate in the contest for new AKASH Subscribers only.</span></span></p>\n\n			<p> </p>\n\n			<p> </p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">10</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">I purchased AKASH connection from 1-31 January 2020 from corporate offer. Am I eligible? </span></span></p>\n\n			<p> </p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Yes! You will be eligible if you activate and recharge no later than 31st January 2020.</span></span></p>\n\n			<p> </p>\n\n			<p> </p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">11</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">I purchased the AKASH connection/STB & activated within 1-31 January 2020 If I recharge for 6 months or 12 months, am I eligible?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Yes, you’ll be eligible. </span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">12</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">I purchased AKASH connection within 1-31 January 2020 through employee fnf offer. Am I eligible to participate?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Yes! You will be eligible if you are not an employee of Beximco Communications Limited or their parents, sibling, spouse, children. But you have to purchase, activate and recharge.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">13</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">How can I participate in the quiz?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">If you have purchased AKASH DTH from our authorized retail outlets, direct sales, Daraz, Referral Campaign, EMI and online within Bangladesh, activated and recharged minimum BDT 399 within the campaign period (1-31 January, 2020) then you are eligible for the campaign quiz. Quiz SMS would be sent to participants on a weekly basis. In the SMS, there will be a toll free number where the subscribers will need to give a missed call. After giving the missed call, soon there will be a call back to the subscriber with the quiz & then the participant will need to answer the question correctly in order to win prizes. </span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">14</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">How will the winners be decided?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">All eligible participants would participate in a weekly quiz and top winners to correctly answer a quiz question will be chosen on the basis of fastest finger first.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">15</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">What will be the CPE Price/STB Price/Package price during the campaign?</span></span></p>\n\n			<p> </p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:57%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">AKASH Connection is available at only BDT 5499 & only STB is available at BDT 3799 now! These prices will also be valid for the campaign period. The BDT 399 subscription fee of AKASH Standard Package will also remain valid. To sum up, there\'s no change in prices or offers during these campaigns.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:7%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">16</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; width:35%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Will the free subscription period of?</span></span></p>\n\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman