i>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Step 4: Prize Delivery- </strong>Jersey will be distributed among the winners at their respective registered addresses, and bat will be distributed at the end of the campaign at Beximco Communications Head Office (Level- 10, SAM Tower, Plot #4, Road #22, Gulshan- 1, Dhaka 1212, Bangladesh.)</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Available Prizes:</u></strong><strong> </strong>New Official Bangladesh National Cricket Team Jersey <em>(For first 50 purchasers every day during the campaign period) and Team Signed Bats (for lucky 3 winners).</em></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">​<strong><u>TERMS & CONDITIONS</u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Cricket Bat and Jersey Giveaway Campaign will remain active from February 26 to March 31, 2020. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The participant must send the SMS as per specified format and from their registered mobile numbers only.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Winner names will be announced only after verification from AKASH team (Beximco Communications Ltd.), and it might take up to 3 working days to finalize and inform the winners. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The purchaser must be Bangladeshi (Nationality) to be eligible for the campaign. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">