\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Yes, more new AKASH DTH connections you buy your chances of winning will be higher.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:75px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">How will the winners be decided? /Based on what the winners will be decided?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:75px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Daily jersey winners list will be finalized based on the participant’s earliest SMS sending time (Earliest first 50 SMS senders) and the 3 bat winners will be decided based on lucky draw after the end of the campaign from the total participant list.    </span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:45px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">What will be the CPE Price/STB Price/Package price during the campaign?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:45px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">AKASH Connection is available at only BDT 5499 & only STB is available at BDT 3199 now! These prices will also be valid for the campaign period. The BDT 399 subscription fee of AKASH Standard Package will also remain valid. To sum up, there\'s no change in prices or offers during these campaign.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:30px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Will the free subscription period of 5 days be available during the campaign?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:30px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Yes, new subscribers during the campaign period will be eligible for the 5-day free subscription period.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:15px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">What are prizes of this campaign?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:15px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">New Official Bangladesh National Cricket Team Jersey (For first 50 purchasers every day during the campaign period) and Bats (for lucky 3 winners).</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:15px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Can a winner win multiple prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:15px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">No, each participant is eligible to win only one prize. </span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">How will the winners know that they have won the prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Day wise winner names will be announced on twice a week and customer will get SMS and call from AKASH team (Winner will get information regarding the prize delivery date). Moreover, day wise winner list (Everyday 50) will be also published twice on Facebook (Names of bat winners will be announced at the end of the campaign).</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:30px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">How will I collect the prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:30px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The winners will get a call from us regarding further details of the prizes and prize collection process.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:30px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Do I need to come physically to collect the prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:30px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Though we’ll deliver the Jersey at your home address, you need to physically come to Beximco Head office to collect the signed Bat. In case of any issue due to unavoidable circumstances, you might have to come physically to collect your Jersey. Moreover, only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled for the Prize, no one else can collect prize on behalf of the subscriber </span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:45px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">What do I need to bring/show to collect prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:45px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The winner might have to show the Winner confirmation SMS from AKASH and have valid identity card and proof of ownership of the registered number in order to collect the entitled prize. Details will be communicated to the winners at the time we call the winners.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:30px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Will I get SMS/any notification if I don\'t win any prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:30px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">No, only the winners will be notified.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Will the winners get any transportation allowance for visiting the designated point to collect the prizes?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">No transportation allowance would be provided to winners when collecting the prize</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:45px; width:25%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Can I get the equivalent cash amount for the prize won?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:45px; width:74%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Prizes won are not transferable and cannot be combined with any other prize or any other offer or discounts or promotions offered by AKASH. Only in the events of exhaustion of existing stock or due to political instability, natural calamities, in such cases prizes will be replaced by other available prizes of same monetary value.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n', '1582707586-34381553.jpg', '1582707586-89728063.jpg', '', 'Promotional', 0, 0, 1, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2020-04-14 20:26:17', '2020-02-26 14:59:46', '', 133);
INSERT INTO `offers` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `description`, `thumb_image`, `banner_image`, `app_image`, `tags`, `show_in_app`, `show_buy_btn`, `state`, `start_time`, `end_time`, `updatedOn`, `createdOn`, `uda`, `serial`) VALUES
(13, 'AKASH Lite', 'akash-lite', '<p>Get 75 of your favorite & popular channels including 20 HD Channels for <strong>BDT 250 monthly</strong> only.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to AKASH Lite Package, 4 add on packs are introduced to offer subscribers the freedom of choice. Design your bouquet as you like!<strong> </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width:100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Add on Packs</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>PRICE BDT Monthly</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>SPORTS ADD ON Pack</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>71</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>ENTERTAINMENT ADD ON Pack</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>75</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>INFOTAINMENT ADD ON Pack</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>45</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>KIDS ADD ON Pack</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>30</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Modalities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Customers will be able to add AKASH Standard or AKASH Lite Pack from the retailer point. Retailer app will have the package selection option during new purchases.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Subscribers can upgrade anytime by calling the call center, he will not need to wait for his validity to expire. When he call our call center, the agents will communicate him the amount he needs to recharge now to convert to AKASH Standard.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Subscriber can upgrade anytime; he will need to recharge the gap amount between AKASH Standard pack fee & remaining unused wallet balance of AKASH Lite. This will be done instantly.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Down-gradation from AKASH Standard to AKASH Lite can only be allowed at the end of the validity of AKASH Standard.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>AKASH Lite package subscribers, too, will get free 1 month & 2 months free subscription respectively if they recharge for 6 & 12 months respectively at once.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Add on packs alone cannot be consumed without valid subscription of AKASH Lite</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Add on packs can be added anytime</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Add on packs can be added or dropped by calling the call center. Auto renewal of add on package will continue unless & until the subscriber calls call center & stops auto renewal.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Add on packs can only be dropped after the expiry of its validity, otherwise un-used wallet balance will be lost.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>When deducting balance, AKASH will first deduct the required balance for AKASH Lite subscription from the wallet. After that, balances will be deducted for the add on packs, based on the hierarchy of these add on packs’ subscription time. The add on which was adopted first will be reactivated upon availability of balance.</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>To adopt any add on packs, subscribes will need to recharge according to the remaining validity of the main package (AKASH Standard or AKASH Lite) of the subscriber. Please call our call center for further details.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Add on packs can be adopted during the free period of AKASH Lite but they will need to pay. Customer needs to recharge the calculated amount for the remaining free validity period of AKASH Lite.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>AKASH Lite subscribers, having add on packs, will lose the un-utilized wallet balance of these add ons if he wants to convert to AKASH Standard package before the expiry of the validity of add on packs. However, he will not lose the un-utilized balance of AKASH Lite in this case.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>For add on packs, no free subscription will be given for recharging for 6 months or 12 months at once.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Before merging to multi tv, if customer had any add on under any of his lite pack, after merging to multi TV, those add ons will not be carried forward & there will be no refund for the unutilized validity for those add ons.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Higher packs should always come earlier in the hierarchy & discount is applicable for second pack and onwards, For instance, if a subscriber has 3 connections: 2 Lite & 1 Standard, then the hierarchy should be like: AKASH STANDARD+ AKASH LITE + AKASH LITE. As there’s no discount on the first connection, therefore, discount will be applicable only on the lower 2 packs. So here, from the table, the discounted subscription fee for the 3 connection in total will be: 400+200+200</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>If a customer converts any of his Lite packs into standard pack, then the hierarchy of the packs will be changed accordingly.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width:100%\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>SN</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Category of FAQ</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>FAQ</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><strong>Answer</strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>AKASH Lite Package</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>How much does the AKASH Lite Package cost monthly? How many channels are there?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>The AKASH Lite Package costs only BDT 250 Monthly! You\'ll get 75 of your favorite channels including 20 true HD Channels!</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>2</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>AKASH Lite Package</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Will I get any free subscription period with AKASH Lite Package?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>If you buy a new AKASH connection with AKASH Lite Package, you\'ll get 5 day free subscription completely free! However, if you are an existing AKASH Subscriber & you adopt or migrate to AKASH Lite Package, you\'ll not get additional free subscription days.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>3</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>AKASH Lite Package</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>I\'m using AKASH Standard now. I want to adopt AKASH Lite Package. When can I migrate?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>You can down-grade to AKASH Lite after your subscription validity has expired. Please call our call center for this operation; you can call anytime, our agents will schedule a future downgradation request on behalf of you in the system at the time of your validity expiry of AKASH Standard for your convenience.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>AKASH Lite Package</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>I\'m using AKASH Standard now and have recharged for 6/12 months recently. I want to adopt AKASH Lite. When can I migrate?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Please call our call center at 16442 for this operation. Our agents will first stop your current billing cycle & then your unutilized balance will be refunded. Then your migration request will be executed immediately.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>5</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>AKASH Lite Package</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>I\'m using AKASH Lite Package now. I want to migrate to AKASH STANDARD PACK. What\'s the procedure & when can I do that?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>You can immediately upgrade your packages. You don\'t need to wait for your billing cycle to be over. Please call our call center at 16442 as the upgradation/migration procedure will be executed through call center.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>6</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>AKASH Lite Package</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>I\'m using AKASH Lite PACK now. I want to migrate to AKASH STANDARD. I have remaining validity for my Lite package. If i upgrade now, how much will i need to recharge for Standard package & how will the amount be calculated?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>You can immediately upgrade your packages. You don\'t need to wait for your billing cycle to be over. Please call our call center at 16442 as the upgradation/migration procedure will be executed through call center.<br />\r\n			For instance, a subscriber is subscribed to AKASH Lite, on his 15th day of subscription, he decides to migrate to AKASH Standard. Now, AKASH Standard costs BDT 399 monthly & customer has unutilized Lite pack balance of BDT (30-15)*(250/30) = BDT 125. Therefore, customer needs to recharge BDT 399 - 125 = 274 to upgrade to AKASH Standard, starting from this 15th day for the next 30 days.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>7</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>AKASH Lite Package</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>If I migrate from AKASH Lite to AKASH STANDARD, will I get any free subscription period/will I get 5 day free period?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>No, existing AKASH Subscribers, migrating to packages will not get any additional free subscription period.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>8</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>AKASH Lite Package</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>I bought a new connection with AKASH Lite & am enjoying 5 day free period. What do I need to do to after the 5 day period to migrate to standard pack subscription?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>You can immediately upgrade your packages. You don\'t need to wait for your billing cycle to be over. Please call our call center at 16442 as the upgradation/migration procedure will be executed through call center.<br />\r\n			Your unused wallet balance can be used for the subscription of higher package; Don\'t worry, you will not lose any unused balance.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>9</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>AKASH Lite Package</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>I want to buy a new connection. At the time of purchase, I want to pick AKASH Lite as my package. What do I need to do?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>You can choose AKASH Lite at the time of new connection purchase. Just inform your retailer about your choice.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>10</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Add on Packs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>I want to add \"ADD ON PACK\" with my AKASH Lite Package. How can I do that? Can I do it immediately from now?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>You can add any add on packs to your AKASH Lite package at any point of time. Please call our call center at 16442 as the add on pack addition/dropping procedure will be executed through call center.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>11</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Add on Packs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Will i get any free subscription period if i add the add on packs?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>No, you will not get any free subscription period when you add your add on packs.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>12</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Add on Packs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Can i only watch add on packs without having Lite package?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>No. Add on packs can only be enjoyed with the valid subscription of Lite package. If your Lite package expires, your add on packs will stop as well even if you have validity for those.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>13</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Add on Packs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Do i need to call call center every month to re-subscribe to my add on packs?/Is there auto renewal facility for add on packs?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Add on packs will be automatically renewed upon availability of balance in your account, after the validity expires. You can only stop add ons by calling our call center; otherwise, auto renewal will continue.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>14</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Add on Packs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Right now I have Add on/s with my Lite pack. I want to drop 1/2 add ons. What\'s the process? Can I do it immediately?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>You can drop add ons after the validity of your add on pack has ended. If you want to drop add on packs before its validity has expired, no refund will be given to your wallet. Please call our call center at 16442 as the add on pack addition/dropping procedure will be executed through call center.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>15</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Add on Packs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>I have Lite package subscription. I can see that if I add all the 4 add ons, the total subscription becomes more than BDT 399 of AKASH Standard Package but channel bouquets are same. </p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>You can add different add ons at different times to your AKASH Lite pack. You have the freedom & you can choose whichever add on you would like according to your preference anytime! We have all the options for you at reasonable prices! However, if you feel adding multiple add ons is less economical for you, you can always upgrade from AKASH Lite to AKASH Standard package, anytime! Just call our call center 16442 to upgrade your package!</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>16</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Add on Packs</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>I just activated my add-on pack, and the validity is different from the validity of my base package. What amount do I have to recharge to activate for my add-on pack for the next month?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>The validity of your add-on packs will be synced in the second month. For this, you will need to recharge the required amount for the difference between the validity of your base pack and the validity of the add-on pack. For example, if you have a Lite/Lite Plus pack validity till 31<sup>st</sup> June, and you activate your add-on on 15<sup>th</sup> June, your add-on validity will be till 15<sup>th</sup> July. The validity will be synced in your next recharge, and you will not need to recharge the full amount in the second month. If you recharge the required amount for the days between the validity of your add-on and your Lite/Lite Plus pack, your add-on will be renewed automatically. In the next months, you will have the same validity for your base pack and your add-ons, and will have to recharge the full amount for activation.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>17</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>AKASH Lite, Add on Packs & Multi TV</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Do i get any discount on add on packs if my Lite pack is under multi tv connection facility?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>No. There\'s no discount on add on packs with or without multi tv connection facility.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>18</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>AKASH Lite, Add on Packs & Multi TV</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>I have multiple connections & now I want to merge them to multi TV facility. How will the subscription fee be decided? I\'m using AKASH Lite PACK with 1/2 add ons. If I convert to multi TV connection, how will my subscription fee be decided?</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>If you opt for multi TV connections, your higher costing base package between AKASH STANDARD & AKASH Lite PACKAGE will come first in the hierarchy. In this method, your package hierarchy will be decided & you will get discount for your 2nd & 3rd connection. For 2nd connection, AKASH STANDARD & AKASH Lite PACK will cost BDT 300 & BDT 200 respectively & for 3rd connection AKASH STANDARD & AKASH Lite PACK will cost BDT 200 & BDT 200 respectively. For instance, if you have 1 Standard package & 2 Lite packages, your total monthly subscription fee will be BDT 400 + BDT 200 + BDT 200 = BDT 799.<br />\r\n			You will not get any discount on your add on pack.<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			And before merging to multi tv if you had any add on packs, those will be lost when you merge to multi tv, you will not get any refund for remaining validity for your add ons.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '1653563357-90315496.jpg', '1647966016-32173911.jpg', '', 'Product', 0, 0, 1, '2020-05-10 16:00:00', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2022-06-23 11:06:14', '2020-02-29 19:13:25', '', 132),
(14, 'MARCH’20 RECHARGE CAMPAIGN', 'mar-recharge', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><u>Campaign Timeline</u></strong><strong>: </strong>11-31 March </span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><u>Participant Eligibility and Modality</u></strong><strong>:</strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>Anyone who buys AKASH Connection within 11-31 March 2020, activates and recharges at least equal to his one-month subscription amount within the first 5 days of his/her Sub ID generation will get the next month subscription for free.</strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><u>TERMS & CONDITIONS</u></strong></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Anyone who buys AKASH Connection within 11-31 March 2020, activates and recharges at least equal to his one-month subscription amount within the first 5 days of his/her Sub ID generation will get the next month’s subscription for free.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Retailer/Distributor of AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) are not eligible to participate.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Employees of AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.), their parents, siblings, spouses & children are not eligible to participate.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Group Employees of Beximco are eligible to participate in this campaign. </span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">AKASH (Beximco Communications Ltd.) reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">People purchasing product before 11 March 2020, but activating during the campaign period (11– 31 March, 2020) are not be eligible for the campaign.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Subscribers can avail the free one-month subscription only recharges at least equal to his one-month subscription amount within the first 5 days of his/her Sub ID generation regardless of the package (AKASH Standard/ AKASH Lite) he is using. </span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-right:84px; text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20.0pt\">FAQ</span></strong></p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:100.0%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#d9d9d9; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:none; border-top:1px solid black; height:20px; vertical-align:bottom; width:3%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"> </span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#d9d9d9; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:20px; vertical-align:top; width:80%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Question</span></span></strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#d9d9d9; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:20px; vertical-align:top; width:15%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Answers </span></span></strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:56px; vertical-align:top; width:3%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">1</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:56px; vertical-align:top; width:80%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">What is MARCH\'20 Recharge Campaign?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:56px; vertical-align:top; width:15%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Anyone who buys AKASH Connection within 11-31 March 2020, activates and recharges at least equal to his one-month subscription amount within the first 5 days of his/her Sub ID generation will get the next month subscription for free.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:3%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">2</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:80%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">How long is the duration of this MARCH\'20 Recharge campaign?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:15%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">The MARCH\'20 Recharge campaign is valid from 11-31 March 2020</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; vertical-align:top; width:3%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">3</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; vertical-align:top; width:80%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">If I purchase only STB, will I be eligible to participate in MARCH\'20 Recharge campaign?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; vertical-align:top; width:15%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Yes, if you purchase a new connection / Multi TV within the campaign period, activate and recharge at least equal to one-month subscription amount within 5 days of Sub ID creation then you are eligible to participate.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; vertical-align:top; width:3%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">4</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; vertical-align:top; width:80%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">I\'m a current subscriber of AKASH. Am I eligible to participate?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; vertical-align:top; width:15%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Only on a purchase of a new connection / Multi TV within the campaign period, activating and recharging minimum one month\'s subscription amount within 5 days of Sub ID creation you are eligible to participate.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:3%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">5</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:80%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Do I need to recharge after activating my connection to participate in this MARCH\'20 Recharge campaign?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:15%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Yes, you have to recharge at least equal to one-month subscription amount within the first 5 days of your Sub ID generation to participate.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:3%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">6</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:80%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">I\'m an employee of AKASH/Beximco Communications Limited. Will I be eligible for MARCH\'20 Recharge campaign?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:34px; vertical-align:top; width:15%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">No, you are not eligible to participate in the MARCH\'20 Recharge Campaign</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:53px; vertical-align:top; width:3%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">7</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:53px; vertical-align:top; width:80%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">I’m an employee of Beximco Group. Am I eligible?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:53px; vertical-align:top; width:15%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Yes, if you purchase a new connection / Multi TV within the campaign period, activate and recharge at least equal to one-month subscription amount within 5 days of Sub ID creation then you are eligible to participate.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:81px; vertical-align:top; width:3%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">8</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:81px; vertical-align:top; width:80%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">I am currently using AKASH Standard package am I eligible for the MARCH\'20 Recharge campaign?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:81px; vertical-align:top; width:15%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span st