:97px; vertical-align:top; width:20%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">I am currently using AKASH Standard package am I eligible for the Cashback Campaign August\'20?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:97px; vertical-align:top; width:76%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">YES! Only on purchasing a new connection (within the campaign period Cashback Campaign August\'20), activating and recharging for a month customer would get a cashback equivalent to the recharge amount BDT 399/249 for the subscribed package that s/he has subscribed after the end of the free trial period of 5 days. The cashback amount would be given in his AKASH account. </span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:92px; vertical-align:top; width:2%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">7</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:92px; vertical-align:top; width:20%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">I am currently using AKASH Lite package am I eligible for the Cashback Campaign August\'20?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:92px; vertical-align:top; width:76%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">YES!  Only on purchasing a new connection (within the campaign period Cashback Campaign August\'20), activating and recharging for a month customer would get a cashback equivalent to the recharge amount BDT 399/249 for the subscribed package that s/he has subscribed after the end of the free trial period of 5 days. The cashback amount would be given in his AKASH account.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:106px; vertical-align:top; width:2%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">8</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:106px; vertical-align:top; width:20%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">If I purchase through EMI on Online will I be eligible for the Cashback Campaign August\'20?</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:106px; vertical-align:top; width:76%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">Yes, only on purchasing a new connection (within the campaign period 16-31 August\'20), activating and recharging for a month customer would get a cashback equivalent to the recharge amount BDT 399/249 for the subscribed package that s/he has subscribed after the end of the free trial period of 5 days. The cashback amount would be given in his AKASH account.</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:41px; vertical-align:top; width:2%px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\">9</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px sol