(28, 'AKASH FEST', 'akash-fest-sep20', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH always strives to make the magical AKASH experience the most rewarding experience for you!&nbsp; AKASH Connection is now available at only BDT 4,499 at a special promotional offer. To spread happiness &amp; the rewarding experience, even more, we have launched &quot;AKASH Fest&quot;. Anyone who purchases a new AKASH connection from 1st September - 30th September 2020, activates &amp; recharges a minimum of BDT 399/249 will be eligible to participate in this campaign to win from 20 exciting prizes per week so hurry up &amp; buy an AKASH Connections!</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> 1<sup>st</sup> September- 30<sup>th</sup> September 2020 </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Participant Eligibility Criteria: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone buying AKASH DTH from AKASH&rsquo;s authorized retail outlets, direct sales and online within Bangladesh, and activating &amp; recharging a minimum of BDT 399/249 for the month of September 2020. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Modality:</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><u>Weekly Contest: </u>All new subscribers who have bought and recharged a minimum of BDT 399/249 for AKASH* in the 1<sup>st</sup> week of September will have to correctly answer a question through a quiz to be conducted via automated Interactive voice response (IVR) and the first 20 to correctly answer in the shortest possible time will be selected as the winner on the basis of fastest finger first. Next week onwards (i.e. 2<sup>nd</sup> to 4<sup>th</sup> week of September 2020), AKASH will select the next set of winners out of eligible participants in the same process described above. The winner and participant of a single week are not eligible to participate in the quiz for upcoming weeks of the month of September unless the winner and/or participant buys a new AKASH DTH connection in the remaining week. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">SMS containing a toll-free number for eligible participants to callback would be sent on September 8<sup>th</sup>, September 15<sup>th</sup>, September 22<sup>nd</sup>, October 6<sup>th,</sup> and eligible participants would have to give a missed call in the provided number and answer a single question and the winner would be selected on Fastest Finger First basis. Participants would be allowed a maximum of 24 hours to participate from the time of eligibility confirmation SMS sent to provide their answer.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Winner Announcement:</strong> Through SMS and Facebook page of AKASH DTH</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>RULES</u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Subscriber must activate and recharge for a 1-month subscription to be eligible for the AKASH FEST SEPT&rsquo;20 quiz, eligible participants will get an SMS, they have to give a &lsquo;missed call&rsquo; on the provided number to take part in the quiz. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The quiz will be based on an Interactive voice response (IVR) and the participant needs to follow the instructions and respond accordingly.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">There will be 1 question for the weekly prize contest.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Participants must participate in the contest within the next 24 hours from the time they received the eligibility confirmation SMS. A late response will result in disqualification. &nbsp;</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A list of <u>Top 20</u> winners will be published on a weekly basis. Winner names will be announced based on the number of right answers and based on the fastest response time. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Subscriber groups enjoying reduced product prices (STB/CPE) will not be eligible for this cashback offer. (i.e: Employee, employee fnf, dealer, etc.)</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">​</span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>TERMS &amp; CONDITIONS</u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;<u>&ldquo;AKASH FEST&rdquo; </u>campaign will be held from 1<sup>st</sup> September &ndash; 30<sup>th</sup> September 2020. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The special promotional price of BDT 4,499 will remain valid until further notice.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The purchaser will get 10 meters length of cable with every unit of AKASH DTH CPE that contains STB, Dish, Remote, LNB, etc.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">During the AKASH FEST campaign, the monthly subscription price will remain BDT 399 for the AKASH Standard package and BDT 249 for the AKASH Lite package. A minimum of 1-month of Subscription Fee (i.e. BDT 399/249) must be recharged to be eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Other special promotion EMI purchases will be eligible for the AKASH FEST campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Anyone buying, AKASH DTH from authorized retail outlets and online (incl. through EMI option and direct sales) within Bangladesh, and activating &amp; recharging for the month on September 2020 are eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Subscribers who bought AKASH DTH before September 2020 and activating and recharging in the month of September will not be allowed to participate in the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Existing AKASH DTH subscribers or inactive customers are not eligible to participate in the campaign. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Only the valid registered subscriber will be entitled to the Prize, no one else can collect the prize on behalf of the subscriber. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">People purchasing AKASH DTH on 30<sup>th</sup> September 2020, but recharging on 6<sup>th</sup> October 2020 or later will not be eligible for the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The entitled winner can collect their prizes from the nearest regional offices on the pre-specified date of AKASH.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Prizes won are not transferable and cannot be combined with any other prize or any other offer or discounts or promotions offered by AKASH. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">All offers (e.g. Specific Model of TV) are subject to availability, it might not be available due to exhaustion of existing stock or due to political instability, natural calamities, in such cases prizes will be replaced by other available prizes of the same monetary value. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The winner needs to show the Winner confirmation SMS from AKASH and have a valid identity card and proof of ownership of the registered number in order to collect the entitled prize. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">No transportation allowance would be provided to winners when collecting the prize. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">By participating, the subscriber/purchaser agrees to be bound by these Terms &amp; Conditions. Subscriber /purchaser must comply with these Terms &amp; Conditions to be able to receive a prize at the end of this campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">All customers have to sign the SAF/Letter of Acknowledgment at the time of purchasing AKASH DTH. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend, and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH shall not be liable for any loss, damage or injury suffered or sustained (even if caused by negligence) as a result of accepting and/or using the prize, except for any liability which cannot be excluded by law.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH accepts no responsibility for late, lost, or misdirected SMS or other communications. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH assumes no responsibility for any failure to receive a claim or for inaccurate information or for any loss, damage, or injury as a result of technical or telecommunications problems, including security breaches. If such problems arise, then AKASH may modify, cancel, terminate or suspend the prize handover process. </span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">​</span></span></p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"Table\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:100.0%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#d9d9d9; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:20px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Question</span></strong></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"background-color:#d9d9d9; border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:20px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Answer</span></strong></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">How long is the duration of this campaign?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The AKASH Fest will run for the entire month of September! You have to purchase an AKASH Connection, activate &amp; recharge within the specified time frame to participate in this campaign.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">If I purchase only STB, will I be eligible to participate?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Yes! If you purchase the full AKASH connection or only the STB, activate &amp; recharge minimum BDT 399/249, you&#39;ll be eligible to participate in the campaign! You&#39;ll have to buy the STB or the full connection within 30th September 2020 otherwise you won&#39;t be eligible. </span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">If I purchase the full connection or the STB on 30th September when do I have to recharge to be eligible?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">If you purchase the full connection or the STB on 30th September you can recharge within 5th October within the five days trial period. </span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">I&#39;m a current subscriber of AKASH. Am I eligible to participate?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">No, only subscribers purchasing the full connection or the STB from 1st September to 30th September are eligible to participate. If you have purchased AKASH before September, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional connections or STBs during 1st to 30th September 2020!</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">I&#39;m a current subscriber of AKASH. Will I be eligible to participate if I recharge within September month?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">No, only subscribers purchasing the full connection or the STB from 1st September to 30th September are eligible to participate. If you have purchased AKASH before September, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional connections or STBs during 1st to 30th September 2020!</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:1.25in; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">I bought AKASH Connection/STB before 1st September 2020 but my installation has been completed in September &amp; I recharged on September am I eligible for the campaign?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:1.25in; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">No, only subscribers purchasing the full connection or the STB from 1st September to 30th September are eligible to participate. If you have purchased AKASH before September, you can still participate in the campaign by buying additional connections or STBs during 1st to 30th September 2020!<br />\n			<em>When a customer places an order via call or FB the day his payment is done the purchase would be considered then, once he recharges for the month of September he or she will be eligible for the campaign. </em></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">I was a Real VU subscriber. Will I be eligible to participate?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:40px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Any Bangladeshi citizen will be eligible to participate if he buys a new AKASH Connection or STB within 1st to 30th September &amp; activates &amp; recharges a minimum BDT 399/249 within 11:59 PM of 5th October 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">I&#39;m an employee of AKASH/Beximco Communications Limited. Will I be eligible to participate?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Employees of Beximco Communications Limited, their parents, siblings, spouses &amp; children are not eligible to participate. However, employees of other concerns of Beximco group are eligible to participate.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">If I purchase through EMI within 1st to 30th September, will I be eligible?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Yes! You will be eligible if you purchase full AKASH connection or STB through EMI, Online or any authorized retail points within 1st to 30th September 2020 &amp; activate &amp; recharge a minimum BDT 399/249 no later than 5th October 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">If I purchase STB/full AKASH Connection through online, will I be eligible?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Yes! You will be eligible if you purchase full AKASH connection or STB through EMI, Online or any authorized retail points within 1st to 30th September 2020 &amp; activate &amp; recharge a minimum BDT 399/249 no later than 5th October 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">I purchased AKASH connection in September from corporate offer. Am I eligible to participate?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:60px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Yes! You will be eligible if you activate &amp; recharge a minimum BDT 399/249 no later than 5th October 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:1.25in; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">I purchased the AKASH connection/STB &amp; activated in September. If I recharge more than BDT 399/249 recharge for 6 months or 12 months, am I eligible?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:1.25in; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Yes! You will be eligible if you activate &amp; recharge a minimum BDT 399/249 no later than 5th October 2020.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">I purchased AKASH connection in September through employee fnf offer. Am I eligible to participate?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:80px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">You will be eligible if you are not an employee of Beximco Communications Limited or their parents, sibling, spouse, children.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:140px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">How can I participate in the quiz?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:140px; width:77%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Subscribers purchasing, activating &amp; recharging each week will be eligible to participate. SMS containing a toll-free number for eligible participants to callback would be sent on September 8th, September 15th, September 22nd, October 6th and eligible participants would have to give a missed call in the provided number and answer a single question and winner would be selected on Fastest right answer basis. Eligible Participants will have to respond within a maximum time of 24 hours after getting the SMS.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:100px; width:23%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-seri