(29, 'GP Star Campaign', 'gpstar-10', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>Campaign Offer </strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">GP Star campaign is a joint campaign which is designed to give the GP Star users of Grameenphone extra benefit while using or buying AKASH connection. GP STARs will enjoy 10% Cashback on MRP of AKASH DTH on the subscriber’s AKASH account & Free 3 & 2 month’s subscription for recharging 12 & 6 months recharge respectively when the subscriber does the recharge in one transaction.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:  </strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">10% Cashback offer (12/10/2020 - 31/03/2021) </span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Recharge Offer (12/10/2020 - 31/03/2021) </span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>Offer Eligibility: </strong>During the campaign period </span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>For New connection Cashback</strong></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Customer needs to be a GP Star</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">To avail the offer customer needs to write AKASH & send the SMS to 29000 port.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">AKASH RMN and GP Star Number must be the same </span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>For Recharge Offer</strong></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Customer needs to be a GP Star</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">To avail the offer customer needs to recharge then write AKASHRE & send the SMS to 29000 port.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">AKASH RMN and GP Star Number must be the same</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>Terms & Conditions </strong></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">To be eligible for these offers, GP Star customers must fulfill the offer eligibility criteria during campaign period</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">To avail the recharge offer, GP Star customers’ needs to recharge the full subscription amount in one transaction first and then send the SMS to the designated port number.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">It would take 10 working days for the customers to receive the recharge offer after sending the SMS.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">It would take 10 working days for the customer to receive the cashback on CPE after the installation is done in his/her home.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:14.6667px\">GP Star Customers can have a maximum of 3 connections against their GP Star RMN.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Subscriber’s RMN and GP Star number must be same.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">A subscriber can only avail the 6 months offer 2 timers and 12 months offer 1 time during the campaign period.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">To avail the 10% cashback offer on MRP of AKASH Regular (BDT 4,499) CPE and AKASH Basic (BDT 3,999) CPE, customers need to send SMS to the designated port to check for eligibility.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Any amount of money given under this campaign cannot be encashed by the beneficiary.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Customer cannot avail both GP Star offer and any other offer at the same time.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">AKASH accepts no responsibility for late, lost or misdirected SMS or other communications. AKASH assumes no responsibility for any failure to receive a claim or for inaccurate information or for any loss, damage or injury as a result of technical or telecommunications problems, including security breaches. If such problems arise, then AKASH may modify, cancel, terminate or suspend the prize handover process.</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">FAQ</span></strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>What is GP Star Campaign?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans. GP Star campaign is a joint campaign which is designed to give the GP Star users of Grameenphone extra benefit while using or buying AKASH connection. GP STARs will enjoy 10% Cashback on MRP of AKASH DTH on the subscriber’s AKASH account & Free 3 & 2 month’s subscription for recharging 12 & 6 months recharge respectively when the subscriber does the recharge in one transaction. </span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>How long is the duration of this campaign?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans. 12/10/2020 – 31/03/2021</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>How can I avail this offer?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans. To avail this offer, you must be a GP Star customer. If you want to buy a new AKASH connection then write AKASH and send it to 29000 and if you want to avail the recharge offer then write AKASHRE and send it to 29000. To avail the recharge offer, GP Star customers need to recharge first then send the SMS to the designated port number.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>I bought AKASH connection before the campaign start date, will I be eligible for this offer?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans. No, to be eligible for the CPE cashback you need to buy AKASH connection during the campaign period and follow the eligibility criteria. To avail the recharge offer, GP Star customers need to recharge first then send the SMS to the designated port number.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>When will I receive my CPE cashback offer?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans. It will take 10 working days after your installation to get the CPE cashback offer.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>When will I receive the recharge offer?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans. It will take 10 working days for you to receive the offer, after you recharge and send SMS.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>I have a GP Star number but my RMN is different, will I be eligible for the recharge offer?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans. No, to be eligible for the offer your GP Star number and AKASH RMN must be same.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>I bought AKASH from online store with my GP Star number, but didn’t send any SMS. Will I be eligible for the offer?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans. Yes! After buying from the online store, you can send the SMS to the designated number fulfilling offer eligibility. After you receive the call from AKASH call center, you can inform that you already purchased a new AKASH connection and ask them for the cashback offer.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>I\'m an employee of AKASH/Beximco Communications Limited. Will I be eligible to participate?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans. Yes! An employee of AKASH/Beximco Communications Limited will be eligible for this as long as they are also GP Star and fulfill other offer criteria.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>Can I get both GP Star and Referral offer?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans.  No, You can not avail both GP Star offer and any other offer at the same time.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>If I purchase Full AKASH Connection online, will I be eligible?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Yes! After buying from online, you can send the SMS to the designated number fulfilling offer eligibility. After you receive the call from the AKASH call center, you can inform that you already purchased a new AKASH connection and ask them for the cashback offer.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>I am a retailer/Distributor of AKASH. Am I eligible for this contest/How can I participate in this contest?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans. Yes! You can participate in the contest if you are also a GP Star and fulfill other offer criteria.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong>If I purchase multiple connections, will I receive cash back for every connection?</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">Ans. Yes! You will receive cashback for every new connection as long as they are against your GP Star RMN and you fulfill other criteria.</span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n', '1602604468-65202166.jpg', '1602604468-32935051.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2020-10-13 20:35:12', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-03-01 13:43:43', '2020-10-13 20:38:52', '', 117),
(30, 'AKASH Basic Set Top Box', 'basic-set-top-box', '<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">To make DTH service more available for mass people of Bangladesh, AKASH has brought a new affordable full connection &ldquo;AKASH Basic&rdquo; for only <strong>BDT 3,999</strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"img-fluid\" src=\"//static.akashdth.com/assets/images/akash-basic-box-word.png\" /></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The STB MRP of <strong>BDT 2,499</strong> will be same for all subscriber groups (i.e. Employee, employee FnF, group employee) for AKASH BASIC STB.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Additionally, AKASH has brought to you a special recharge offer if you recharge at once for 6 or 12 months. Recharge for 6 months and get 1 month additional subscription completely FREE! Recharge for 12 months and get 2 months additional subscription completely FREE!</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The minimum purchase amount needed to be eligible for EMI facility is BDT 5,000. As AKASH connection with AKASH BASIC STB is BDT 3,999, you will need to buy subscription with the connection to avail EMI facility.</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Here are the 6 &amp; 12 month EMI costs with applicable minimum required subscriptions for EMI:</span></p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width:90%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>COMBINATION</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>6 month EMI Amount</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>12 month EMI Amount</strong></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>\n			<p><span 