ly:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">Yes!&nbsp; buy from online, and pay the special price with AMERICAN EXPRESS card. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">I am a retailer/Distributor of AKASH. Am I eligible for this campaign? </span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">Ans. No</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">If I purchase multiple connections, will I receive cash back for every connection?</span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#4c4c5b\">Ans. Yes since the cashback offer is on recharge, if the customers recharges 6/12 months for his multi tv connection he would get the cashback in his account with 10 working days of the recharge. &nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n', '1612329371-46281420.jpg', '1612329371-15976722.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-02-03 11:10:18', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-02-03 11:16:11', '2021-02-03 11:16:11', '', 105);
