(51, 'Boishakhi Offer', 'boishakhi-offer-21', '<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">To double your joy of festivity this Boishakh, AKASH is giving its customer BDT 800 cashback when they purchase AKASH connection from AKASH Website through the &ldquo;<strong>Boishakhi Campaign</strong>&rdquo;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">08/04/2021 &ndash; 20/04/2021</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Offer Eligibility: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer needs to purchase AKASH from AKASH Website (<a href=\"https://akashdth.com/\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\">https://akashdth.com/</a>) during campaign timeline.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer will need to recharge for 1 month according to their subscription package during the campaign period.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer will need to register to Selfcare with their new SUB ID within 27<sup>th</sup> April, 2021. (<a href=\"https://akashdth.com/#register\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\">https://akashdth.com/#register</a>)</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Modality</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Customers has to buy AKASH connection from AKASH website within the campaign period.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To avail the BDT 800 Cashback, customers have to activate the connection, recharge for a month and register in self-care. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; All the cashback amount would be given on 29<sup>th</sup> April, 2021. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The recharge and installation has to be done within 27<sup>th</sup>&nbsp; April to avail the cashback. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; After 27<sup>th</sup> April the recharge would be considered invalid, and no cashback would be given in reference to the same. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Any amount of cashback given under this campaign cannot be uncashed or transferred by the beneficiary. And it&rsquo;s not related to any other campaign or discount of AKASH </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">7.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; One customer can avail one offer at a time in terms of AKASH CPE purchase.</span></span></p>\n', '1618499058-42988625.jpg', '1618499058-15480179.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2021-04-08 11:55:18', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-04-15 21:38:43', '2021-04-08 10:33:17', '', 95);
