; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:208px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Sports Addon</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:208px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">71</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:208px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Infotainment Pack 2</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; vertical-align:top; width:208px\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">21</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Upon successful activation of new addon, customers will get cashback equal to one-month recharge price of that addon.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> 21 &ndash; 30 Apr 2021 (10 days)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Terms and Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">All the customers will be eligible for this offer if they have not already taken all possible addons.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Addons should be newly onboarded and activated during the campaign period to avail this offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Recharging any INACTIVE addons will not be included in this offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If anyone already has one addon, he can take other addons to avail this offer. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If anyone already has all the possible addons onboarded, he will NOT be included in the offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If a customer is in 6 months or 12 months billing cycle and add any new addon, he/she will get the cashback equal to one-month recharge of the addon.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Cashbacks will be given to customer&rsquo;s AKASH Account within 05 May 2021.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customer will NOT get any cashback if he removes the addon pack before the campaign ends.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">FAQ:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q1. Am I eligible for this campaign?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: If you already haven&rsquo;t taken all the possible addons (Infotainment pack 2 for AKASH Standard and All 5 addons for AKASH Lite), you are Eligible.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q2. What is the offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: By Activating and recharging any new Addon during the campaign, you will get 100% cashback on one-month price of that addon.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q3. How can I activate any new addon?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: By calling 16442, through AKASH Self-care and Direct Activation SMS.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q4. How will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback will be given in your AKASH Account within 05 May 2021.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q5. I already have Entertainment Addon (or any other), but I didn&rsquo;t recharge it. Will I get the cashback if I recharge now?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: No. But you can get the cashback if you take any other cashback (Like Sports or Kids etc.)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q6. I am currently availing 1-month free offer for 6 months recharge, how can I get this offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: You need to recharge for 6 months for an Addon to activate it. Then you will get the cashback equal to 100% of 1-month recharge of your addon.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q7. What will be the cashback amounts?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: For Entertainment Addon: BDT 75</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Infotainment Addon: BDT 45</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Sports Addon: BDT 71</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Kids Addon: BDT 30</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Infotainment pack 2: BDT 21</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q8. Can I avail other campaigns and offers if I take this offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of any other offers or campaigns.</span></span></span></p>\n', '1618829774-40845487.jpg', '1618829774-2848862.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-04-20 23:55:27', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-04-19 16:56:14', '2021-04-19 16:56:14', '', 92),
(55, 'EID UL FITR DISCOUNT OFFER', 'eid-ul-fitr-discount', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">With a view to spread joy and happiness, AKASH has launched an exclusive campaign for the customers. On the occasion of Eid-ul-Fitr, from 22 April &ndash; 14 May, 2021 you can purchase a new AKASH connection from any AKASH touch point and get 500 BDT net discount on AKASH Basic and AKASH Regular. During the campaign period you can now purchase <strong>AKASH Basic</strong> on <strong>3,499 BDT</strong> and <strong>AKASH Regular</strong> on <strong>3,999 BDT</strong>. So, hurry up and grab this exclusive offer!</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline: </strong>22 April &ndash; 14 May, 2021<strong>&nbsp; </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><a name=\"_Hlk69850095\">Customers have to buy AKASH connection from any AKASH touch point during the campaign period (22 April &ndash; 14 May, 2021).</a></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><a name=\"_Hlk69850172\">500 BDT net discount on the MRP for both AKASH Basic and AKASH Regular connection for the customers. The campaign period price will be 3,499 BDT for AKASH Basic and 3,999 BDT for AKASH Regular.</a></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><a name=\"_Hlk69850252\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:#212529\">This offer is applicable for new whole connection purchase, discount cannot be availed for only Set Top Box purchase.</span></span></a></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:#212529\">2 or 3 combo new connection purchase at once will get 1,000 BDT or 1,500 BDT discount respectively.</span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n', '1619002751-226436.jpg', '1619002751-37400048.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2021-04-21 23:55:17', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-04-21 16:59:11', '2021-04-21 16:59:11', '', 91),
(56, 'EID UL FITR DISCOUNT & CASHBACK OFFER FOR WEBSITE PURCHASE', 'eid-ul-fitr-discount-cashback', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH has launched an exclusive campaign with a view to double the joy and happiness for the customers. On the occasion of Eid-ul-Fitr, from 22 April &ndash; 14 May, 2021 you can purchase a new AKASH connection from AKASH website and get 500 BDT net discount on AKASH Basic and AKASH Regular. On top of the discount, you will also get cashback of 200 BDT on 1<sup>st</sup> month recharge of subscription pack. So, hurry up and grab this exclusive offer!</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline: </strong>22 April &ndash; 14 May, 2021<strong>&nbsp; </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">500 BDT net discount on the MRP for both AKASH Basic and AKASH Regular connection for the customers. The campaign period price will be<strong> 3,499 BDT</strong> for <strong>AKASH Basic</strong> and <strong>3,999 BDT</strong> for <strong>AKASH Regular</strong>.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Additional <strong>200 BDT cashback</strong> will be given to the customers purchasing AKASH only through AKASH website after activation and 1<sup>st</sup> month of subscription pack recharge.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customers have to buy AKASH connection from AKASH website only during the campaign period (22 April &ndash; 14 May, 2021) to avail the cashback offer</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This offer is exclusively for the purchase from AKASH website only.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">It would take 10 working days for the customers to receive the cashback amount in their AKASH account from recharge date.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The recharge to avail cashback amount for website purchase has to be done within 21 May, 2021.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">After 21 May, 2021 the recharge would be considered invalid, and no cashback would be given in reference to the same. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Any amount of cashback given under this campaign cannot be uncashed or transferred by the beneficiary. And it&rsquo;s not related to any other campaign of AKASH.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:#212529\">This offer is applicable for new whole connection purchase, discount cannot be availed for only Set Top Box purchase.</span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n', '1619003327-97716673.jpg', '1619003327-52769373.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2021-04-21 23:55:24', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-04-21 17:08:47', '2021-04-21 17:08:47', '', 90),
(57, 'Eid Entertainment Fest', 'eid-entertainment-fest', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">This Eid will come with full of Entertainment for AKASH Lite Subscribers as AKASH brings 100% cashback on New Entertainment Addon package activation. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Upon successful activation of New Entertainment Addon, customers will get cashback equal to one-month recharge price of the Addon.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Price of Entertainment Pack for one month: </span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">BDT 75</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> 1 &ndash; 15 May 2021 (15 days)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Terms and Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">All the AKASH Lite Customers will be eligible for this offer if they have not already taken Entertainment Addon.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Addons should be newly onboarded and activated during the campaign period to avail this offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Recharging any INACTIVE addons will not be included in this offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If anyone has other addons except Entertainment, he can avail this offer. </span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If a customer is in 6 months or 12 months billing cycle and add any new addon, he/she will get the cashback equal to one-month recharge of the addon.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Cashbacks will be given to customer&rsquo;s AKASH Account </span><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">within 23 May 2021.</span></strong></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customer will NOT get any cashback if he removes the addon pack before the campaign ends.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">FAQ:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q1. Am I eligible for this campaign?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: If you already haven&rsquo;t taken Entertainment addon, you are Eligible.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q2. What is the offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: By Activating and recharging Entertainment Addon newly during the campaign, you will get 100% cashback on one-month price of the addon.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q3. How can I activate any new addon?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: By calling 16442, through AKASH Self-care and Promotional Activation SMS.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q4. How will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback will be given in your AKASH Account within 23 May 2021.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q5. I already have Entertainment Addon, but I didn&rsquo;t recharge it. Will I get the cashback if I recharge now?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: No.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q6. I am currently availing 1-month free offer for 6 months recharge, how can I get this offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: You need to recharge for 6 months for the Addon to activate it. Then you will get the cashback equal to 100% of 1-month recharge of your addon.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q7. What will be the cashback amounts?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: BDT 75</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q8. How will I know I got the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: You will be notified through SMS after cashback adjustment given. You can also check your account balance through &ldquo;Help&rdquo; button of remote option or through your self-care account.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Q9. Can I avail other campaigns and offers if I take this offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of any other offers or campaigns.</span></span></span></p>\n', '1619693983-78305645.jpg', '1619693983-41959293.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-04-30 23:55:44', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-04-29 16:59:43', '2021-04-29 16:59:43', '', 89),
(58, '2 Years Anniversary BDT 600 Cashback Campaign', '2years-anniversary-600-cashback', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">On the 2<sup>nd</sup> year anniversary purchasing AKASH is made more rewarding with BDT 600 Cashback on first month recharge. A customer who buys AKASH connection from retail point, distributor and AKASH website, activates and recharges a minimum BDT 249/399 for a month will get BDT 600 cashback. The amount of the cashback is fixed BDT 600 would not be dependent on the amount of subscription of the fist package taken.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:black\">Campaign Timeline:</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> 19/05/2021 &ndash; 31/05/2021</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">Terms &amp; Conditions</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">1. Customers can buy AKASH connection from retail stores, distributors and AKASH website within the campaign period.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">2. To avail the BDT 600 cashback, customers have to activate the connection, recharge for a month to avail the cashback.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">3. Customers to receive the cashback amount in their AKASH account on 9<sup>th</sup> June 21.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\">