’s AKASH Account within 05 August 2021.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Customer will NOT get any cashback if he removes the add on pack before the campaign ends.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">FAQ:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q1. Am I eligible for this campaign?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: If you already haven’t taken all the possible add-ons (Infotainment pack 2 for AKASH Standard, all add-ons except Entertainment for AKASH Lite Plus, and All 5 addons for AKASH Lite), you are Eligible.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q2. What is the offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: By Activating and recharging any new Add on pack during the campaign, you will get 100% cashback on one-month price of that addon.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q3. How can I activate any new addon?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Through AKASH Self-care or by calling AKASH Hotline number 16442.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q4. How will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback will be given in your AKASH account within 05 August 2021.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q5. I already have Entertainment Add on (or any other), but I didn’t recharge it. Will I get the cashback if I recharge now?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: No. But you can get the cashback if you take any other cashback (Like Sports or Kids add on etc.)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q6. I am currently availing 1-month free offer for 6 months recharge, how can I get this