 style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of any other offers or campaigns.</span></span></span></p>\n', '1625578744-733233.jpg', '1625578744-51737343.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-07-06 23:55:21', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-07-06 20:34:22', '2021-07-06 19:39:05', '', 78),
(70, 'Eid ul Adha Recharge Fest', 'eid-ul-adha-recharge-fest', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">On this holy occasion of Eid ul Adha, AKASH brings more happiness to its subscribers. Any customer recharging exactly <strong>BDT 601</strong> within the campaign period will get a fixed <strong>BDT 60</strong> cashback to his/her AKASH Account. The customer can avail this offer as many times as he/she wants during the campaign period. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Besides, if the customer recharges through AKASH Selfcare, he/she will get <strong>additional BDT 40</strong>. That means, by recharging exactly <strong>BDT 601</strong> through <strong>AKASH Selfcare</strong> customer will get <strong>BDT 100 Cashback</strong>. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Registration link for AKASH Selfcare</strong>: t.ly/kEkj</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 11 &ndash; 31 July, 2021</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions:</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Cashbacks will be given to customer&rsquo;s AKASH account within 7 working days from recharge.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 601 for the offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A subscriber can recharge as many times as he/she wants. There&rsquo;s no restriction on the number of recharges a subscriber can make during the campaign period. Every time he/she can avail this offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer will get additional BDT 40 if he/she recharges through AKASH Selfcare. In that case total Cashback amount will be BDT 100.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Successive recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 400 and then BDT 201, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 601 in a single recharge.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This campaign does not depend on other campaigns as any customer can avail other campaign offers as well as Eid ul Adha Recharge Fest campaign offer by recharging exactly BDT 601 in his/her AKASH account within campaign period. </span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n', '1626074313-651440.jpg', '1626074313-46264336.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-07-12 12:15:00', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-07-12 13:29:29', '2021-07-12 13:18:33', '', 77),
