a customer down-migrates his package to AKASH Lite or AKASH Lite Plus at any time during the campaign (i.e., from 13 Sep to 30 Sep), he/she will NOT be eligible for this campaign.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customer can upgrade their packages from AKASH web self-care or by calling 16442.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customer must migrate to get the cashback. Only recharging the migration amount will not initiate the offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">FAQ:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">What is Standard Upgrade Campaign?</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans</span></u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">: If you are an AKASH Lite or AKASH Lite Plus customer, you can get a cashback by upgrading your package to a higher pack: BDT 100 for upgrading from Lite to Standard, BDT 50 for Lite plus to Standard</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">How can I migrate/upgrade to AKASH Standard package?</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans</span></u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">: through AKASH web self-care or by calling 16442</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">I have bought AKASH in this month, am I eligible for this offer?</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans</span></u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">: NO. New customers on-boarded in September 2021 will not be eligible for this offer.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"4\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Why didn&rsquo;t I get the cashback after migrating from AKASH Lite to AKASH Standard?</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans</span></u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">: If you have bought AKASH after August 31, or if your package is INACTIVE after upgradation, you will NOT get the cashback.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"5\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">When will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans</span></u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">: Cashback will be given to your AKASH Account within 15 working days of migration.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"6\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">I have recharged BDT 399, why didn&rsquo;t I get the cashback?</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Ans</span></u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">: Only recharge will not initiate the offer. You must migrate your package by calling 16442 or through Web self-care.</span></span></span></p>\n', '1631452523-50357458.jpg', '1631452524-60019554.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-09-12 23:55:41', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-09-12 19:15:24', '2021-09-12 19:15:24', '', 68),
(81, 'Online Sales Campaign', 'online-sales-campaign', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You can now get attractive offers on top of our ongoing campaigns if you purchase AKASH connection from AKASH website. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Campaign Timeline: 14/09/2021 – 31/10/2021</span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Offer</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Basic</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">1.             Full CPE + 2 Month AKASH Standard (BDT 4,797)</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">You’ll receive 1 Month AKASH Standard subscription fee free</span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Product Link – <a href=\"https://akashdth.com/buy-AKASH/Basic/cpe-1-standard2-offer\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\">https://akashdth.com/buy-AKASH/Basic/cpe-1-standard2-offer</a></span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">2.             Full CPE + 6 Month AKASH Standard (BDT 6,393)</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">On top of our existing 6 month recharge campaign offer customer will receive 1 Month AKASH Standard subscription fee free</span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Product Link - <a href=\"https://akashdth.com/buy-AKASH/Basic/cpe-1-standard6-offer\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\">https://akashdth.com/buy-AKASH/Basic/cpe-1-standard6-offer</a></span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Campaign Condition</span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer will only be able to purchase this product bundle from AKASH website.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer will receive the cashback amount within 10 working days.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">For the 6 month’s recharge offer, customer will receive existing AKASH offer of 1 month and subscription fee equivalent of 1 month’s AKASH Standard Package. So in total customer will be able to enjoy 2 free month’s AKASH Standard. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer’s RMN must be same as the contact number given while purchasing AKASH connection.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n', '1631613472-85780433.jpg', '1631613473-78223596.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2021-09-14 16:30:00', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-10-31 19:48:54', '2021-09-14 15:57:53', '', 67),
(82, 'GP STAR Cashback Offer', 'gp-star-cashback-offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">AKASH in collaboration with Grameenphone brings an exclusive offer for their GP Star Customers. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">During the campaign period, Star Customers can get additional BDT 200 cashback if they have successfully bought and recharged minimum 1 month subscription, on top of the existing &ldquo;আকাশ কিনে চলুন T20 বিশ্বকাপে&rdquo; campaign. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">To avail this offer, GP Star customers must: Type <strong>AKASH</strong> and send SMS to <strong>29000</strong>.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 16 September &ndash; 12 October, 2021 (Recharge within 19 October, 2021)</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms and Conditions:</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customer needs to be a GP Star</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">To be eligible for this offer, GP Star customers must fulfill the offer eligibility criteria during campaign period.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">To avail the cashback offer, GP Star customers need to type <strong>AKASH</strong> and send the SMS to the designated port number 29000. Then customers will receive a reply message on the purchase process.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">An agent from AKASH Call center will call the interested GP Star customer within 24 hours and collect relevant information to process the order.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Cashback to the eligible customers will be disbursed to customers&rsquo; AKASH account within 10 working days </strong>on the condition that subscribers have at least recharged minimum of 1 month subscription fees in one transaction within 19 Oct, 2021 on the new connection that he/she has purchased.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customers can avail this offer on top of the &ldquo;আকাশ কিনে চলুন T20 বিশ্বকাপে&rdquo; campaign offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">GP Star Customers can have a maximum of 3 connections against their GP Star RMN.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Subscriber&rsquo;s RMN and GP Star number must be same</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Existing AKASH subscribers or inactive customers activating their account are not eligible to participate in the campaign</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Subscribers who bought AKASH before September 2021 and activating and recharging on the month of September will NOT be allowed to participate in the campaign.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customers purchasing AKASH Connection from retail point will <strong>NOT</strong> be eligible for this offer even if he/she sends SMS to the designated port. Customers need to confirm their status BEFORE purchase.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Any amount of money given under this campaign cannot be encashed by the beneficiary.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">AKASH accepts no responsibility for late, lost or misdirected SMS or other communications. </span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">AKASH assumes no responsibility for any failure to receive a claim or for inaccurate information or for any loss, damage or injury as a result of technical or telecommunications problems, including security breaches. </span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '1631794401-11505533.jpg', '1631794402-55474321.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-09-16 18:10:02', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-09-16 18:59:18', '2021-09-16 18:13:22', '', 66),
(83, 'Enjoy 20% Discount on Saving VISA Card', 'discount-on-saving-visa-card', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A campaign for AKASH subscribers where they will get 20% discount on monthly subscription fee up to BDT 150 while saving new VISA Card on AKASH DTH<strong> </strong>website/selfcare while recharge. &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> September 22 &ndash; November 30, 2021</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Modality:</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This discount offer starts on September 22, 2021 and shall be valid till November 30, 2021. </span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"2\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">This offer is applicable to any Visa cardholder who has a valid and unexpired Visa Credit, Debit or Prepaid Card issued in Bangladesh, and yet to be saved at AKASH DTH portal.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"3\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The VISA cardholder will enjoy discount only once after saving the card during the campaign period.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"4\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Under the campaign, eligible VISA cardholders will get 20% (Twenty percent) discount <strong>only on the monthly subscription fees</strong> of AKASH DTH up to BDT 150.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"5\" style=\"list-style-type:upper-roman\">\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">The offer will be valid for E-commerce transactions of AKASH Bill/Subscription payment through <a href=\"http://www.akashdth.com\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\">www.akashdth.com</a> by website &amp; Selfcare option only and all the VISA card transactions during this period</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>FAQ</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>What is the offer? </strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>- 20% discount</strong> <span style=\"color:#202124\">on </span><strong><span style=\"color:black\">AKASH monthly subscription fee </span></strong><span style=\"color:black\">through www.akashdth.com &amp; selfcare option </span><span style=\"color:#202124\">up to BDT 150 by saving VISA card of all banks.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>What is the campaign period?</strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">- 22 September 2021 to 30 November 2021.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Will I get discount with EMI? </strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">- No</span></span></p>\n\n<ol start=\"4\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Where can I avail this offer from? </strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">- The offer is available in webpage bearing the URL <span style=\"color:black\">www.akashdth.com &amp; Selfcare option</span>. This is solely an online campaign.</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"5\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Who is eligible for this campaign?</strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">- All unsaved VISA cardholders (debit/credit/prepaid) before the campaign period will be eligible under this offer.&nbsp; </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"6\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Is there any capping in discount? </strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - BDT 150</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>7. Is there any limit to the number of times that the cardholder will be eligible for the offer? </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">- Yes, once (1) after saving the VISA card during the campaign period.</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"8\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>&nbsp;Is this offer available for both POS and online payment? </strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">- No, the offer is available for only online payment.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"9\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>When will the cardholders receive the discount? </strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">-The cardholder will receive the discount <strong>instantly</strong> while buying the product.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"10\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Is it available for only EBL Visa Cards?</strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - No, the discount is available for all Visa card issued in Bangladesh</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"11\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Is the discount available for previously saved Visa Card?</strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">No, the discount is available for newly saved cards during the campaign</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"12\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Can one user avail the offer more than once with different Visa Cards?</strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">- Yes, the discount can be availed for each Visa card. Per Visa Card one (1) time discount.</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"13\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Can the discount be availed with different user accounts saving the same card?</strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">- No, the discount can be availed once (1) per card on <span style=\"color:black\">www.akashdth.com &amp; selfcare option</span>.</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol start=\"14\">\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Can I avail this discount for purchasing new AKASH connection, accessories etc?</strong></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - No, the discount is only for the payment of AKASH monthly subscription fee through AKASH&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; website or AKASH Selfcare</span></span></p>\n', '1632398008-31668654.jpg', '1632398008-42137261.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-09-23 23:55:54', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-11-07 15:21:12', '2021-09-23 17:53:28', '', 65),
(84, 'ENJOY AKASH WITH “0% EMI”', 'zero-percent-emi', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH has introduced 0% EMI for purchases made through the website and making AKASH connection more accessible through payment convenience. Now, people can buy AKASH Basic and AKASH Regular with 6 months and 12 months EMI. There are 0% EMI plans for website bundle purchases (Connection and Subscription).<strong> </strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH now <strong>removes the extra EMI cost</strong> obstacle for customers who want to avoid single-term payment.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><u>Terms and Conditions</u>:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">0% EMI will be <strong>available for website purchases</strong> with specific bank’s credit cards only.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">No bundle less than BDT 5000 will be eligible for 0% EMI. </span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">EMI Duration: 6 months & 12 months.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The following is the list of banks whose credit cards will be accepted for 0% EMI:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\" style=\"border-colla