(86, 'Clean Feed Blackout Recharge Cashback', 'clean-feed-blackout-recharge-cashback', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">AKASH is launching a cashback campaign for recharging, as all channels are not available currently. AKASH Standard and AKASH Lite Plus Customers will receive a cashback if they recharge the required amount (or above) for their package. For customers who have already recharged before the campaign period, an adjustment will be provided to the customer&rsquo;s account after the end of the month.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> November 1, 12:00AM &ndash; will continue until further notice.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Terms &amp; Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customers will get an instant cashback if they recharge their respective package price, or above during the campaign</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Required recharge amount for the instant cashback for AKASH Standard is BDT 399 and for AKASH Lite Plus, BDT 300.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">The instant cashback amounts will be: BDT 50 for AKASH Standard and BDT 25 for AKASH Lite Plus.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Customers can avail the instant cashback only once during the campaign period.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">The customers who recharged earlier and remained ACTIVE during the November clean feed black out will also get their due adjustment according to their package and the number of days they were active during clean feed blackout. They will receive their cashback after November 30<sup>th</sup>.&nbsp; The maximum adjustment amounts are as follows: AKASH Standard &ndash; BDT 50, AKASH Lite Plus &ndash; BDT 25. If any of these customers recharge and get instant cashback during the campaign period, they will not get further adjustment. </span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Campaign FAQs:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none; width:100.0%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:24px; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Sl No.</span></strong></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:24px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Question</span></strong></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black; height:24px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Answer</span></strong></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:74px; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">1</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:74px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">What is the amount for Cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:74px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:1