ns-serif\">3</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Who will be eligible for the instant cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">All AKASH customers (except for AKASH Lite Subscribers), irrespective of active status, will be eligible for this cashback offer.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">4</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">How many times can I get the instant cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-fami