ht:50px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">When will I receive the cashback after recharging?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:50px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">The cashback will be disbursed to your account instantly.</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:74px; vertical-align:top; width:6%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">7</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:74px; vertical-align:top; width:30%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">I did not recharge during the campaign period, but my account was active. Will I get any offer/cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none; height:74px; vertical-align:top; width:62%px\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">If you did not recharge during the campaign, but were active you will receive an adjustment to your AKASH account. The adjustment/cashback