le=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q2. How many times I can recharge?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You can recharge as many times you want. You will get the cashback for every recharge of BDT 800.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q3. What is the cut off time for the recharge?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You need to recharge within the Match-day for that day’s cashback (From 12:00 AM to 11:59 PM)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q4. What will be the cashback amount?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: For every BDT 800 recharge on the match day, cashback will be equal the total runs scored by Bangladesh</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q5. When will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: within 5 working days from recharge, cashback will be given to your AKASH account.</span></span></span></p>\n', '1637254378-24939134.jpg', '1637254378-93250774.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-11-18 21:55:16', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-11-18 22:53:22', '2021-11-18 19:54:19', '', 55),
(94, 'Winter Recharge Offer', 'winter-recharge-offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> Any customer recharging 501 taka within the campaign period will get a fixed BDT 50 cashback to their wallet. The customer can avail this offer as many times as he/she wants during the campaign period. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> 23 November 2021 to 30 November 2021 (8 days)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Terms & Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Cashbacks will be given to customer’s Akash account within 10 working days from recharge.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 501 for the offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">A subscriber can recharge as many times as he/she wants. There’s no restriction on the number of recharges a subscriber can make during the campaign period. Every time he/she can avail this offer.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Successive recharges will NOT be counted & treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 400 and then BDT 101, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 501 in a single recharge.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">The cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign FAQs:</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q1. How can I avail 50-taka cashback offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: By recharging BDT 501 to your Akash account in a single recharge within 23 Nov 2021 to 30 Nov 2021. </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q2. Where will the customer get this cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback will be given to your Akash wallet.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q3. When I can avail this offer?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You can avail this offer by recharging BDT 501 to your Akash account in a single recharge withi<em>n 23 Nov 2021 to 30 Nov 2021.</em></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q4. When will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Cashbacks will be given within 10 working days from recharge. You will get an SMS confirmation after that.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q5. Can I avail this offer more than once?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer as many times as you want within the campaign period by recharging 501 taka every time.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q6. During campaign, if I recharge fractionally (not at a time) to make it BDT 501, will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Fractional recharges will NOT be counted & treated as a single recharge. For instance, if you recharge BDT 400 and then BDT 101, you will not get the cashback. You need to recharge BDT 501 at a single recharge to get the cashback.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q7. What if I recharge more than BDT 501?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You can only avail this offer if your recharge amount is exactly BDT 501. You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than BDT 501 </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q8. Will other offers be applicable for me if I avail this offer or vice versa?</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of all other offers.</span></span></span></p>\n', '1637684314-60860343.jpg', '1637684314-5972754.jpg', '', 'offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-11-22 23:55:30', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-11-23 22:18:34', '2021-11-23 20:02:02', '', 54),
(95, '50 Years of Victory Campaign', '50-years-victory-campaign', '<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH has launched an exclusive campaign for the customers from 1 - 31 December on the occasion of 50 years of Bangladesh&rsquo;s victory where anyone can purchase new AKASH connection from any AKASH touchpoint, retail, AKASH website, partner store at <strong>500 BDT discount</strong>. The campaign period price will be <strong>3,499 BDT</strong> for AKASH Basic. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> 1 &ndash; 31 December, 2021</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Terms &amp; Condition: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">Customers have to buy AKASH connection from AKASH touch points or AKASH website within the campaign period to avail the offer.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">500 BDT net discount on the MRP for AKASH Basic connection for the customers. The campaign period price will be </span><strong><span style=\"color:black\">3,499 BDT</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> for AKASH Basic.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">The discount offer is not available on the STB rather on the whole connection (CPE) of AKASH Basic.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:black\">For single CPE purchase through strategic partner stores this offer will be applicable if they are not offering a better offer than 500 BDT discount. Otherwise,for bundle offer pack they will have their own campaign and this discount offer will not be applicable. </span><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n', '1638275949-45310730.jpg', '1638275970-27301736.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2021-11-30 23:55:44', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-12-14 11:19:58', '2021-11-30 18:40:08', '', 53),
(97, 'Victory Month Recharge Offer', 'victory-day-recharge-offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">On the occasion of 50 years of our Victory, AKASH brings a lucrative Recharge offer for its valued customers.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 1 December 2021 to 31 December 2021 (31 days)</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Campaign Brief:</strong> Any customer recharging BDT 1000 taka from 1 December to 31 December 2021 will get a 16% cashback in their AKASH Account. The customer can avail this offer as many times as s/he wants during the campaign period. </span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">On top of that, if a customer recharges BDT 1000 through NAGAD App or NAGAD USSD (only once), he will get additional 16% Cashback in his NAGAD wallet.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions:</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">All the customers of AKASH are eligible for this offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Cashbacks will be given to customer&rsquo;s Akash account instantly after recharge.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 1000 for the offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">A subscriber can recharge as many times as he/she wants. There&rsquo;s no restriction on the number of recharges a subscriber can make during the campaign period. Every time he/she can avail this offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Successive recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 400 and then BDT 600, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 1000 in a single recharge.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">The cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">On top of everything, if a customer recharges this BDT 1000 from NAGAD App or NAGAD USSD, s/he will get additional 16% Instant cashback in his Nagad wallet.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Nagad cashback will be available only <strong>ONCE</strong> from a single Nagad Account, but the customer can still get 16% cashback in AKASH account for as many BDT 1000 recharges as s/he wants.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Nagad offer is valid from 13 Dec 2021 to 31 Dec 2021.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Nagad offer can be availed only recharging from NAGAD App or NAGAD USSD. Customer will not be eligible for NAGAD Cashback if he/she makes payment through merchant website or aggregator payment gateway.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Campaign FAQs:</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q1. How can I avail 16% cashback offer?</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: By recharging BDT 1000 to your Akash account in a single recharge within 1 Dec 2021 to 31 Dec 2021. At the same time.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q2. Where will the customer get this cashback?</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Cashback will be instantly given to your Akash wallet.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q3. When I can avail this offer?</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: You can avail this offer by recharging BDT 1000 to your Akash account in a single recharge withi<em>n 1 December 2021 to 31 December 2021.</em></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q4. When will I get the cashback?</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Cashbacks will be given Instantly to your AKASH Wallet. You will be notified through SMS</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q5. Can I avail this offer more than once?</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer as many times as you want within the campaign period by recharging 1000 taka every time.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q6. During campaign, if I recharge fractionally (not at a time) to make it BDT 1000, will I get the cashback?</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Fractional recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if you recharge BDT 900 and then BDT 100, you will not get the cashback. You need to recharge BDT 1000 at a single recharge to get the cashback.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q7. What if I recharge more than BDT 1000?</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: You can only avail this offer if your recharge amount is exactly BDT 1000. You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than BDT 1000</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q8. Will other offers be applicable for me if I avail this offer or vice versa?</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of all other offers.</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q9. What is NAGAD offer for this Campaign?</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: You will get additional 16% Cashback in your Nagad Wallet if you recharge BDT 1000 in AKASH DTH through NAGAD app or USSD. That means, Recharging BDT 1000 from Nagad, you will get 16% Cashback in AKASH Account and another 16% Cashback in NAGAD wallet. But Nagad Offer can be available only once from a single Nagad Account. Nagad Offer is valid from 13 Dec to 31 Dec 2021.</span></span></p>\n', '1638461741-11866807.jpg', '1638461741-80615533.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-12-01 21:55:54', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-12-14 17:38:48', '2021-12-01 19:45:06', '', 52),
(98, 'Selfcare Campaign', 'self-care-campaign', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Any customer who will newly register for AKASH web selfcare in the month of December will get a 10% cashback up to BDT 100 on their first recharge through selfcare. </span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Registration link for Akash Web Selfcare: t.ly/kEkj</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 01 – 31 December 2021 (31 days)</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Terms & Conditions:</strong></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer must register for the web selfcare in December 2021. Registration before 1 December or after 31 December will not be eligible for cashback.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer must recharge through AKASH web self-care portal to avail this offer.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">To get the cashback, recharge from selfcare has to be within 31 December 2021.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer will NOT get the cashback if he/she recharges from AKASH website only without signing in to Selfcare.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Cashbacks will be given to customer’s Akash account within 10 working days after recharge.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">A customer can get maximum BDT 100-taka cashback. That means, from BDT 1 to BDT 1,000, customer will get 10% Cashback. Recharging above BDT 1,000 will give a fixed cashback of BDT 100.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">A customer can avail this offer only <strong>for the first recharge through selfcare</strong> during the campaign.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">The cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Communication Media: </strong>Digital, Barker Channel, Website</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Campaign FAQs:</strong></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q1. How can I avail self-care cashback offer?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: By registering newly for AKASH web selfcare in December and recharging any amount through web selfcare within December 2021.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q2. Where and when will the cashback be given?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Cashback will be given to your Akash account within 10 working days of recharge.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q4. Can I avail this offer more than once?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: NO. You can avail this offer only for the first recharge through selfcare within December.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q5. What is the required amount to be recharged for the offer?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: You can only avail this offer by recharging any amount through Web self-care.</span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q6. Will other offers be applicable for me if I avail this offer or vice versa?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of all other offers.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q7. Will I get this offer if I recharge from AKASH website without signing in to Selfcare?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: NO, you must log in to AKASH self-care to avail this offer.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q8. Is there any maximum limit of cashback?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Yes, Maximum cashback will be BDT 100 for this offer.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q9. What will be the cashback amount?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: For recharging from BDT 1 to BDT 1,000, cashback amount will be 10% of the recharge. Above BDT 1,000, cashback amount will be fixed BDT 100.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q10. I have registered for web self-care, but never recharged through selfcare, If I recharge now, will I get the cashback?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: NO. This offer is only for the new registrations in Selfcare in December.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q11. Will I get the cashback my first recharge is in January?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: No. First recharge from selfcare has to be within December 2021.</span></p>\n', '1638957391-4210862.jpg', '1638957391-91631409.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-12-02 16:05:44', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-12-08 15:56:31', '2021-12-02 16:08:14', '', 51),
(99, 'City Bank Amex Save the Card', 'city-bank-amex-offer', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Now you can enjoy exclusive savings on subscription fee recharge of your AKASH account as well as on new connection purchase when you save your City Bank American Express Credit card while payment on AKASH website. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> 1 -31 December, 2021</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>For subscription recharge</strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">25% off up to BDT 200 while saving the card. From AKASH website and Selfcare customer can enjoy 25% discount up to BDT 200 while saving City Bank American Express Credit Card. Discount on the bill payment will be instant. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>For new purchase</strong>, customers purchasing AKASH connection will get an exclusive discount while saving City Bank American Express Credit Card on payment. This offer is only available on <strong>AKASH Full Setup (1 connection)</strong> on AKASH&rsquo;s website which is 1 AKASH Basic CPE unit. To know about the offer, you can call City Bank&rsquo;s Customer Care hotline 16234.<br />\nYou can avail the discount from this link: <a href=\"https://akashdth.com/buy-AKASH/Basic/cpe-1-amex\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\">https://akashdth.com/buy-AKASH/Basic/cpe-1-amex</a></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Discount can only be enjoyed once while saving the City Amex Credit card during the campaign period.</span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Previously saved card cannot enjoy the discount. Only newly saved card during campaign period can avail the offer.</span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">The offer will be valid for E-commerce transactions of AKASH Bill/Subscription payment through <a href=\"http://www.akashdth.com\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\">www.akashdth.com</a> by website &amp; selfcare option only and all the City Amex Credit card transactions during this period.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n', '1639459498-54029058.jpg', '1639459499-33181175.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2021-12-14 11:20:38', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-12-14 11:27:10', '2021-12-14 11:24:59', '', 50),
(100, 'New Year Campaign', 'new-year-campaign-2022', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A campaign <a name=\"_Hlk75863641\">on welcoming the new year, from 1 - 31 January, 2022 you can purchase AKASH from any AKASH touchpoint, retail, AKASH website, partner store at <strong>BDT 500 discount</strong></a>. <a name=\"_Hlk75863694\">The campaign period price will be </a><strong>BDT 3,499 </strong>for AKASH Basic. </span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><a name=\"_Hlk75863679\"><strong>Campaign Timeline:</strong> 1 – 31 January, 2022</a></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms & Condition: </strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Customers have to buy AKASH connection from AKASH touchpoint or AKASH website within the campaign period to avail the offer.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">BDT 500 net discount on the MRP for AKASH Basic connection for the customers. The campaign period price will be </span><strong><span style=\"color:black\">3,499 BDT</span></strong><span style=\"color:black\"> for AKASH Basic.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The discount offer is not available on the STB rather on the whole connection (CPE) of AKASH Basic.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Strategic partners will have their own campaign. For single CPE purchase through strategic partner this offer will be applicable if they are not offering a better offer than 500 BDT discount. Otherwise, for bundle offer pack they will have their own campaign and this discount offer will not be applicable.</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">AKASH reserves all the right to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n', '1640694666-87593303.jpg', '1640694670-789689.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 1, 1, '2021-12-31 23:55:56', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2021-12-28 18:36:04', '2021-12-28 18:31:10', '', 49);
INSERT INTO `offers` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `description`, `thumb_image`, `banner_image`, `app_image`, `tags`, `show_in_app`, `show_buy_btn`, `state`, `start_time`, `end_time`, `updatedOn`, `createdOn`, `uda`, `serial`) VALUES
(102, '2022 New Year Recharge Offer', 'new-year-recharge-offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> 1 January 2022 to 31 January 2022 (31 days)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Happy New Year 2022! To welcome the new year, AKASH brings an exciting cashback offer on monthly recharge.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Any customer recharging BDT 500 taka from 1 January to 31 January 2022 will get a BDT 50 Instant cashback in their AKASH Account. The customer can avail this offer as many times as s/he wants during the campaign period. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">On top of that, if the customer recharges BDT 500 through <strong><em>tap</em></strong> App or USSD (only once), s/he will get additional BDT 50 Cashback in his <strong><em>tap</em></strong> wallet.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Terms & Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">All the customers of AKASH are eligible for this offer.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">BDT 50 Cashback will be given to customer’s <strong>AKASH</strong> account instantly after recharge.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 500 for the offer.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">A subscriber can recharge as many times as he/she wants. There’s no restriction on the number of recharges a subscriber can make during the campaign period. Every time he/she can avail this offer. </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Successive partial recharges will NOT be counted & treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 400 and then BDT 100, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 500 in a single recharge.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">AKASH</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">On top of everything, if a customer recharges this BDT 500 from <strong><em>tap</em></strong> App or USSD, s/he will get additional BDT 50 cashback in his <strong><em>tap</em></strong> wallet.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">tap</span></em></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> cashback will be available only <strong>ONCE</strong> from a single <strong><em>tap</em></strong> Account, but the customer can still get BDT 50 cashback in AKASH account for as many BDT 500 recharges as s/he wants.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">tap</span></em></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> offer can be availed only recharging from <strong><em>tap</em></strong> App or USSD. Customer will not be eligible for <strong><em>tap</em></strong> Cashback if he/she makes payment through merchant website or aggregator payment gateway.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">tap </span></em></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">cashback will be given within 2 working days of recharge.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">AKASH</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign FAQs:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q1. How can I avail BDT 50 cashback offer?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: By recharging BDT 500 to your Akash account in a single recharge within 1 Jan 2022 to 31 Jan 2022.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q2. Where will the customer get this cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback will be instantly given to your Akash wallet. Besides, if the customer recharges through <strong><em>tap</em></strong>, then additional BDT 50 cashback will be given to customer’s <strong><em>tap</em></strong> wallet (Only once)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q3. When I can avail this offer?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You can avail this offer by recharging BDT 500 to your Akash account in a single recharge withi<em>n 1 – 31 January 2022.</em></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q4. When will I get the <strong>AKASH</strong> cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Cashbacks will be given Instantly to your AKASH Wallet. You will be notified through SMS. <strong>tap</strong> cashback will be given within 2 working days in tap wallet.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q5. Can I avail this offer more than once?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer as many times as you want within the campaign period by recharging 500 taka every time. But <strong><em>tap </em></strong>cashback can be availed only once.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q6. During campaign, if I recharge fractionally (not at a time) to make it BDT 500, will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Fractional recharges will NOT be counted & treated as a single recharge. For instance, if you recharge BDT 400 and then BDT 100, you will not get the cashback. You need to recharge BDT 500 at a single recharge to get the cashback.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q7. What if I recharge more than BDT 500?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You can only avail this offer if your recharge amount is exactly BDT 500. You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than BDT 500</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q8. Will other offers be applicable for me if I avail this offer or vice versa?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of all other offers.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q9. What is <strong><em>tap</em></strong> offer for this Campaign?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You will get additional BDT 50 Cashback in your <strong><em>tap</em></strong> Wallet if you recharge BDT 500 in AKASH DTH through <strong><em>tap</em></strong> app or USSD. That means, Recharging BDT 500 from <strong><em>tap</em></strong>, you will get BDT 50 Cashback in AKASH Account and another BDT 50 Cashback in <strong><em>tap</em></strong> wallet. But <strong><em>tap</em></strong> offer can be available only once from a single <strong><em>tap</em></strong> Account.</span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1640859208-51743145.jpg', '1640859208-24749094.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2021-12-31 23:55:07', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2022-01-20 12:07:10', '2021-12-30 16:13:29', '', 48),
(103, 'Language Month 21% Offer on Recharge', 'language-month-21-recharge-offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">On 21<sup>st</sup> February 1952, we, the people of Bangladesh, sacrificed our lives for our mother tongue. This year marks the 70<sup>th</sup> anniversary of that historic movement. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">To commemorate the historic moment, AKASH brings some exciting recharge offers for its customers!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 1 February &ndash; 28 February 2022 (28 days)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Offer:</strong> </span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Any customer recharging <strong>BDT 1952</strong> will get a <strong>21% Instant cashback</strong> in their AKASH Account.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">The customer can avail this offer as many times as he/she wants.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">All the new and existing customers of AKASH are eligible for this offer.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Cashbacks will be given to customer&rsquo;s AKASH account instantly after recharge. You will be notified through SMS.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Customer needs <strong>to recharge exactly BDT 1952 </strong>in his/her AKASH account within the campaign period to avail the offer.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Cashback amount for BDT 1952 recharge will be <strong>BDT 409.92</strong> <strong>(21% of 1952)</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">A subscriber can available this offer during this campaign.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">A subscriber can recharge as many times as he/she wants. There&rsquo;s no restriction on the number of recharges a subscriber can make during the campaign period. Every time he/she will get the cashback.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Successive partial recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 1000 and then BDT 952, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 1952 in a single recharge.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">You can only avail this offer if your recharge amount is exactly BDT 1952. You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than the given amounts.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Customers can avail this offer on top of all other offers.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">AKASH cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '1643610265-34777959.jpg', '1643610265-99726495.jpg', '', 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2022-01-31 23:55:57', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2022-02-01 14:16:31', '2022-01-31 12:24:26', '', 47),
