(116, 'Boishakhi Recharge Offer', 'Boishakhi-Recharge-Offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">14 April 2022 is the first day of Bangla New Year, 1429. In this Boishakh, AKASH brings a Boishakhi Recharge offer for its valued customers!</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 1 April to 30 April 2022 (30 days)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Offer:</strong> </span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Any customer recharging <strong>BDT 1429</strong> will get a <strong>14% Instant Cashback</strong> in their AKASH Account. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">The customer can avail the offer as many times as he/she wants. &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">All the new and existing customers of AKASH are eligible for this offer.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Cashbacks will be given to customer&rsquo;s AKASH account instantly after recharge. You will be notified through SMS.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 1429 in his/her AKASH account to avail the offer.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Cashback Amount</strong> for BDT 1429 recharge will be <strong>BDT 200.06 (14% of 1429).</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">A subscriber can recharge as many times as he/she wants. There&rsquo;s no restriction on the number of recharges a subscriber can make during the campaign period. Every time he/she will get the cashback.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Successive partial recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 1400 and then BDT 29, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 1429 in a single recharge within 1-30&nbsp;April 2022.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customers can avail this offer on top of all other offers.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">You can only avail this offer if your recharge amount is <em>exactly</em> BDT 1429. You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than the given amounts.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '1648720260-54827973.jpg', '1648720260-21497512.jpg', NULL, 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2022-04-01 00:05:29', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2022-04-11 11:14:39', '2022-03-31 15:51:00', '', 36),
(117, 'Nagad Boishakhi Recharge Offer', 'nagad-boishakhi-recharge-offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">In this Bangla New year 1429, AKASH and Nagad together have brought an exciting recharge benefit for the customers.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> 5 April 2022 to 30 April 2022 (26 days)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Offer:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> Any customer recharging BDT 1429 to his AKASH account from Nagad App or USSD will get BDT 150 instant cashback to his Nagad Account. Besides, AKASH’s regular Boishakhi Recharge Offer of 14% cashback to AKASH account will also be available for BDT 1429 recharge. That means, a customer can get up to BDT 350.06 benefit on BDT 1429 recharge in his AKASH account.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Terms & Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">All the new and existing customers of <strong>AKASH</strong> are eligible for this offer.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Cashbacks will be given to <strong>Nagad</strong> account instantly after recharge.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 1429 in his/her <strong>AKASH</strong> account from <strong>Nagad App or USSD</strong> to avail the offer.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Cashback amount in Nagad account will be <strong>BDT 150</strong></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">A subscriber can avail this Nagad cashback <strong><em>only Once.</em></strong></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Successive partial recharges will NOT be counted & treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 1400 and then BDT 29, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 1429 in a single recharge.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Besides, customers will get 14% instant cashback (BDT 200.06) to his AKASH account for recharging BDT 1429 from any payment channel. </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">AKASH</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> <strong>and Nagad</strong> reserve all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign FAQs:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif; font-size:18px\">Q1. How can I avail Nagad Boishakhi Recharge offer?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: By recharging BDT 1429 from NAGAD App or USSD to your Akash account in a single recharge within 5 Apr 2022 to 30 Apr 2022.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q2. Where will the customer get this cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: BDT 150 Cashback will be instantly given to your Nagad Account. And BDT 200.06 cashback will be given to your AKASH account.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q3. When I can avail this offer?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You can avail this Nagad offer from 05 April to 30 April 2022.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q4. When will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Cashbacks will be given Instantly to your AKASH and Nagad Account. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q5. How much cashback will I get?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: BDT 150 Cashback will be instantly given to your Nagad Account. And BDT 200.06 cashback will be given to your AKASH account.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q6. Can I avail this offer more than once?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Nagad cashback will be available only once in a Nagad account. But AKASH Cashback will be available as many times as customer wants.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q7. During campaign, if I recharge fractionally (not at a time) to make it BDT 1429, will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Fractional recharges will NOT be counted & treated as a single recharge. For instance, if you recharge BDT 1400 and then BDT 29, you will not get the cashback. You need to recharge BDT 1429 at a single recharge to get the cashback.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q8. What if I recharge more than 1429?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You can only avail this offer if your recharge amount is exactly BDT 1429. You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than the given amounts.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q9. Will other offers be applicable for me if I avail this offer or vice versa?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of all other offers.</span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1649739539-7367258.jpg', '1649739539-77936608.jpg', '1649824593-92132108.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 0, 1, '2022-04-12 10:55:24', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2022-04-26 10:29:30', '2022-04-12 10:58:59', 'Recharge', 35),
(118, 'Special 100% Cashback offer', 'special-100-cashback-offer', '<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">In the month of Ramadan, AKASH is giving 100% cashback offer to some of its selected customers. If a customer recharges his package and activate it within the campaign period, he will get a 100% cashback on his package price. Cashback will be disbursed throughout the next 3 months in the following ways: 1<sup>st</sup> month: 50%, 2<sup>nd</sup> Month: 25%, and 3<sup>rd</sup> Month: 25%</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Offer Duration:</strong> 12 April 2022 to 30 April 2022</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Offer Eligible Customers:</strong> Only those customers who will receive offer SMS, RVC or phone call about the offer. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms & Conditions:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Only customers who will get the offer SMS, RVC or phone call from AKASH will be eligible for the offer</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer must recharge and remain active during the campaign to avail the cashback.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Cashback will be given as per customers existing package. For AKASH Standard, 100% cashback will be equal to BDT 400, for AKASH Lite Plus: BDT 300, for AKASH Lite: BDT 250</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><em>100% Cashback will be disbursed fractionally for next 3 months</em></strong>. In the first month after recharge, cashback amount will be 50% of the package price. In the second month, customer will receive another 25% and in the third month, s/he will receive the rest 25%.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">During these 3 months of cashback disbursement, customers need to keep their subscriptions ACTIVE to get the cashback.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">If a customer stops recharging and becomes INACTIVE at any point of this 3-month period, s/he will miss the following months’ cashbacks. For example: If an AKASH Standard customer recharges during the campaign period, he will receive 50% i.e., BDT 200 cashback in the first month. In the next month, if the customer does not recharge and becomes INACTIVE, he will miss the rest 50% cashback.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Cashback will be disbursed within the first 10 working days of every month for the next 3 months after campaign.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">if the customer changes his package before recharging for the offer, the customer will get the cashback according to the new package. But he changes the package after activation, then the benefit will be as per the previous package.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer can change the billing cycle to 6 or 12 months and can enjoy the LDP Offer benefits, but 100% cashback offer will be only based on the package subscription fee for 30 Days (i.e.- 400,300,250 etc.)</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all the rights to change, extend or cancel this offer at any time.</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Offer FAQ:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q1. What is April’22 100% Cashback Campaign for Selective Churn Customers?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Segoe UI Symbol\",sans-serif\">➢</span> We are offering selective customers 100% Cashback on recharge subscription fee only to activate the connection. If customers recharge within 30th Apr’22, then 50% Cashback will be given by 1<sup>st</sup> 10 working days of May’22. Rest benefits will be given if the customer remain active in May & Jun’22, then Benefits will be added by 1st 10 days of next Jun’22 (25% cashback) & Jul’22 (rest 25% cashback).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q2. Who will be eligible for 100% Cashback Offer?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Segoe UI Symbol\",sans-serif\">➢</span> Only those customers who will receive offer SMS, RVC or phone call about the offer. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q3. What if the Customer wants to upgrade the Package before or after activation?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Segoe UI Symbol\",sans-serif\">➢</span> Before activation if the package is changed then the customer will get the cashback according to the upgraded package. But if the change is after activation, then the benefit will be as per the previous package.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q4. What if the customer wants to downgrade the package?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Segoe UI Symbol\",sans-serif\">➢</span> There will be no cashback offer if the package is downgraded.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q5. What will be the 100% cashback disbursement process?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Segoe UI Symbol\",sans-serif\">➢</span> 100% Cashback will be disbursed in 3 slots within the 1st 10 working days of months, 50% Cashback on May’22, 25% on Jun’22, 25% on Jul’22.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q6. If the customer change to 6/12months billing cycle, then what will be the offer?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Segoe UI Symbol\",sans-serif\">➢</span> Customer can change the billing cycle and can enjoy the LDP Offer benefits, but 100% cashback offer will be only based on the package subscription fee for 30 Days (i.e.- 400,300,250 etc.)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q7. Where cashback amount will be adjusted?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Segoe UI Symbol\",sans-serif\">➢</span> In customers Akash Account.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q8. Will customers get any other offer benefits during this Campaign?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Segoe UI Symbol\",sans-serif\">➢</span> If eligible for other