(125, 'Cricket Season Recharge Offer', 'cricket-season-recharge-offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">We have an exciting cricket season from July onwards. Before touring Zimbabwe in August, Bangladesh will be facing West Indies in ODI and T20 in July. There is an Asia Cup Cricket scheduled from August. And finally, we have T20 Cricket World Cup in October 2022. To the utter delight of the valued sports loving customers of AKASH, we bring an exclusive recharge offer for the customers. Any customer recharging for 3-month i.e., BDT 1200 in AKASH Standard will get additional 1-month Free. This will let the customers enjoy all the cricket events till T20 Cricket World Cup.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 1 July 2022 to 31 July 2022 (31 days)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Offer:</strong> Any customer recharging BDT 1200 in AKASH Standard will get a BDT 400 Instant cashback in their AKASH Account. A customer can avail this offer <strong>only Once</strong> during this campaign.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">All the new and existing customers of <strong>AKASH</strong> are eligible for this offer.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Cashbacks will be given to customer&rsquo;s <strong>AKASH</strong> account instantly after recharge.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 1200 in his/her <strong>AKASH Standard </strong>account to avail the offer.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Offer will not be applicable to <strong>AKASH Lite / AKASH Lite Plus.</strong> Customers from these packages need to <strong><em>upgrade to AKASH Standard</em></strong> before recharging to avail this offer.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">After recharging BDT 1200, instantly BDT 400 cashback will be given to customer&rsquo;s AKASH Account as 1-month free AKASH Standard subscription.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A subscriber can avail this offer <strong><em>only once</em></strong> during this campaign.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Successive partial recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 1100 and then BDT 100, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 1200 in a single recharge.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>AKASH</strong> cashback amount can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>AKASH</strong> reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign FAQs:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q1. How can I avail Cricket Season Recharge offer?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: By recharging BDT 1200 to your Akash Standard package in a single recharge within 1 July 2022 to 31 July 2022.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q2. What is the offer?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: By recharging 3-month i.e., BDT 1200 in <strong>AKASH Standard</strong>, you will get BDT 400 Instant cashback to your AKASH account which will be equivalent to 1-month AKASH Standard subscription.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q3. Where will the customer get this cashback?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback will be instantly given to your Akash Account. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q4. When I can avail this offer?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: You can avail this offer from 01 July to 31 July 2022.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q5. When will I get the <strong>AKASH</strong> cashback?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: Cashbacks will be given Instantly to your AKASH Account. You will be notified through SMS.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q6. How much cashback will I get?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: For Recharging BDT 1200, you will get BDT 400 cashback.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q7. Can I avail this offer more than once?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: <strong>NO</strong>, you can avail this offer <strong><em>only once</em></strong> during the campaign period</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q8. I am an AKASH Lite Plus Customer. Will I get this offer?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: AKASH Lite or Lite Plus customers need to <strong>upgrade to AKASH Standard </strong>before recharging to avail this offer. Recharging while subscribed to Lite/Lite plus will not earn any cashback.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q9. I&rsquo;ve already recharged BDT 400 this month. Will I get this offer?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer once for recharging BDT 1200.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q10. I have recharged AKASH BDT 1200 in AKASH Lite Plus. If I upgrade to AKASH Standard package now, will I get the cashback?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: <strong>NO.</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q11. During campaign, if I recharge fractionally (not at a time) to make it BDT 1200, will I get the cashback?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: Fractional recharges will <strong>NOT</strong> be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if you recharge BDT 1100 and then BDT 100, you will <strong>NOT</strong> get the cashback. You need to recharge BDT 1200 in a single recharge to get the cashback.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q12. What if I recharge more than 1200?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: You can only avail this offer if your recharge amount is exactly BDT 1200. You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than the given amounts.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q13. Will other offers be applicable for me if I avail this offer or vice versa?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of all other offers.</span></span></p>\r\n', '1656610293-83539740.jpg', '1656610293-56041605.jpg', '1656610293-82043212.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 1, 1, '2022-06-30 23:55:41', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2022-06-30 23:39:40', '2022-06-30 23:31:33', 'Recharge', 27),
