fer at any time.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>FAQ:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q1: How can I avail this offer? / What is the offer?           </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: All AKASH Subscribers will get BDT 200 discount on minimum BDT 1000 recharge through DBL VISA card from MyAKASH App/AKASH website (<a href=\"http://www.akashdth.com\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\">www.akashdth.com</a>). </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q2: Where will the customer get this discount?  </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: The discount amount will be adjusted with the customer’s  Dhaka Bank’s <strong>VISA – Gold, Platinum, Signature & MasterCard -Titanium Credit Cardholders only</strong> (All Credit Cards of Dhaka Bank), hence BDT 800 will be deducted from the customer’s DBL visa card while paying (for BDT 1000).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q3: Can I avail this offer more than once?            </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: Customer can avail the offer unlimited time throughout the campaign period.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q4: During campaign, if I recharge fractionally (not at a time), will I get the cashback?          </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: No. Customer needs to recharge minimum BDT 1000 in a single transaction.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q5: What is the conditions and benefit amount for Multi TV?      </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: BDT 200 for BDT 1000 recharge in a single transaction.</span></span></p>\r\n', '1666780313-98070678.jpg', '1666780314-8195868.jpg', '1666763556-48287837.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 0, 1, '2022-10-19 23:55:57', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2022-10-26 16:31:54', '2022-10-19 17:31:14', 'Recharge', 16);
