(138, 'ICC Men’s T20 World Cup Match Day Offer', 'ICC-Men’s-T20-World-Cup-Match-Day-Offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">On the occasion of ICC Men’s T20 World Cup T20 2022, AKASH brings a special cashback offer for its valued customers. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Any customer recharging BDT 1200 on an ICC Men’s T20 World Cup match day will receive a cashback equal to winning team’s total score of that day.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign Duration:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\"> 22 October – 13 November 2022 (only on ICC Men’s T20 World Cup match days)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Terms & Conditions:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Customer must recharge exactly BDT 1200 in his AKASH account.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Customer needs to recharge within the Match-day for that day’s cashback (From 12:00 AM to 11:59 PM)</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Cashback amount will be equal to the winning team’s total of that match on ICC Men’s T20 World Cup.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Cashback amount will be equal to the highest team total among the teams playing on that day. Example: If there are 2 matches, India vs Scotland and NZ vs Namibia, Cashback will be equal to the highest team total among these 4 countries.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Cashback will be given within 5 working days after the match.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">A customer can recharge as many times as he wants. For every recharge of BDT 1200, he will be entitled for the cashback</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">This offer will be applicable on top of all other offers applicable for the customer.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">If any match gets abandoned without a single ball bowled, customers recharging BDT 1200 will get BDT 120 cashback.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">If the match remains incomplete, cashback will be equal to highest team total of the completed part of the match.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">If there is no ICC Men’s T20 World Cup match on a day, there will be no cashback for that day.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Campaign FAQs:</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q1. How can I avail ICC Men’s T20 World Cup Recharge offer?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: By recharging exactly BDT 1200 to your Akash account on the ICC Men’s T20 World Cup match day, you will get the cashback equal to the highest Team total of that day (Winning team’s score)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q2. How many times I can recharge?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You can recharge as many times you want. You will get the cashback for every recharge of BDT 1200.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q3. What is the cut off time for the recharge?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: You need to recharge within the Match-day for that day’s cashback (From 12:00 AM to 11:59 PM)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q4. What will be the cashback amount?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: For every BDT 1200 recharge on the match day, cashback will be equal the highest Team total of that day (Winning team’s score)</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q5. When will I get the cashback?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: within 5 working days, cashback will be given to your AKASH account.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"> </p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Q6: For multiple matched in a single day what will be the cashback amount.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif\"><span style=\"font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback amount will be equal to the highest team total among the teams playing on that day. Example: If there is 2 matches, India vs Scotland and NZ vs Namibia, Cashback will be equal to the highest team total among these 4 countries.</span></span></span></p>\r\n', '1666774573-83224002.jpg', '1666350613-83223687.jpg', '1666503848-54032079.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 0, 1, '2022-10-21 23:55:30', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2022-10-26 14:56:13', '2022-10-21 17:10:13', 'Recharge', 15),
(139, 'BDT 500 Savings on New AKASH Connection by EBL Visa Card', 'BDT-500-Savings-on-New-AKASH-Connection-by-EBL-Visa-Card', '<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">EBL Visa cardholders can now enjoy exclusive savings on the occasion of the FIFA World Cup when they purchase new AKASH BASIC connection from AKASH website. Under the campaign, EBL VISA cardholders will get BDT 500 (Five Hundred) discount for E-commerce transactions on new connection purchase from <span style=\"color:black\">MyAKASH App</span>/AKASH website:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://akashdth.com/buy-AKASH/Basic/special-ebl-offer\">Special EBL Offer</a></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">This new connection purchase offer includes 1 month&rsquo;s subscription fee. The total price of this bundle offer is BDT 4899/- (Four Thousand Eight Hundred Ninety-Nine Taka Only) and eligible EBL VISA Cardholder shall pay BDT 4399/- (Four Thousand Three Hundred Ninety-Nine Taka Only) only after availing the discount offer of BDT 500/- (Five Hundred Taka Only).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline: </strong>10 November &ndash; 18 December 2022</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Consumer Offer Modality:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Customer need to purchase a specific combo product of BASIC connection Full CPE with one-month AKASH STANDARD Package at BDT 4,899.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Customer will get BDT 500 discount through EBL VISA card payment. </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Customers need to purchase through MyAKASH App/AKASH website </span>(www.akashdth.com)<span style=\"color:black\">.</span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Customers can avail the offer unlimited time throughout the campaign period. </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">AKASH and EBL reserve all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>FAQ:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q1: Which cards are applicable? </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A: EBL Visa Card</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q2: From where can I avail this offer? (AKASH website/My AKASH App/Self care/ Other websites/ Other apps?)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A: From MyAKASH App/AKASH website: <a href=\"http://www.akashdth.com\" style=\"color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline\">www.akashdth.com</a>.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q3: Is this offer applicable for both POS and online payment?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A: Only online payment</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q4: What is the benefit amount? And how will customers get it? </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A: Customers will get BDT 500 discount through EBL VISA card payment.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q5:Will customer get this offer with EMI?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A: No</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q6: Applicable for any connection purchase? (Full CPE, only STB, Combo 2/3/4 connection etc.)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A: Customers need to purchase an specific combo product of BASIC connection Full CPE with one-month AKASH STANDARD Package at BDT 4,899.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q7: If I only buy STB, will I get benefit in price?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A: No</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q8: How many connections can a customer purchase with same card?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A: Customer can avail the offer for unlimited time within the campaign period.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Q9: Any restriction on saving visa card? </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">A: No</span></span></p>\r\n', '1667992769-48471505.jpg', '1667992769-49231866.jpg', NULL, 'Offer', 0, 0, 1, '2022-11-09 23:55:08', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2022-11-16 10:17:26', '2022-11-09 17:19:30', '', 14),
(140, '11-11 Recharge Campaign', '11-11-Recharge-Campaign', '<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">All AKASH Subscribers will get 11% instant cashback on recharging BDT 1,111.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Campaign Timeline: </strong>11 Nov 2022 &ndash; 30 Nov 2022</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Offer Modality:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">11% (BDT 122.21) Cashback will be given to customer&rsquo;s Akash account instantly after recharge.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 1,111 for the offer.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer can avail this offer only once during the offer period.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Successive recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 500 and then BDT 611, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 1,111 in a single recharge.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Cashback amount in AKASH account can be used for consumption in packages, add on packs etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH reserve all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>FAQ:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q1: How can I avail this offer? / What is the offer?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">A: All AKASH Subscribers will get BDT 11% (BDT 122.21) cashback on BDT 1,111.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q2. Where will the customer get this cashback?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Cashback will be instantly given to your Akash wallet. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q3. When I can avail this offer?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: You can avail this offer by recharging BDT 1,111 to your Akash account in a single recharge from<em> 11 November 2022 to 30 November 2022.</em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q4. When will I get the cashback?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Cashbacks will be given Instantly to your AKASH Wallet. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q5. Can I avail this offer more than once?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: No. AKASH cashback will be available only once for a single AKASH Subscriber ID. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q6. During campaign, if I recharge fractionally (not at a time) to make it BDT 1,111, will I get the cashback?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Fractional recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if you recharge BDT 500 and then BDT 611, you will not get the cashback. You need to recharge BDT 1,111 at a single recharge to get the cashback.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q7. What if I recharge more than BDT 1,111?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: You can only avail this offer if your recharge amount is exactly BDT 1,111. You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than BDT 1,111.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q8. Will other