(144, '12-12 Recharge Campaign', '12-12-Recharge-Campaign', '<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">All AKASH Subscribers will get 12% instant cashback on recharging BDT 1,212.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Campaign Timeline: </strong>01 Dec 2022 &ndash; 31 Dec 2022</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>Offer Modality:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">12% (BDT 145.44) Cashback will be given to customer&rsquo;s Akash account instantly after recharge.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer needs to recharge exactly BDT 1,212 for the offer.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Customer can avail this offer only once during the offer period.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Successive recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 600 and then BDT 612, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge BDT 1,212 in a single recharge.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Cashback amount in the AKASH account can be used for consumption in packages, add-on packs, etc. permitted by AKASH.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">AKASH reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any time.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong>FAQ:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q1: How can I avail this offer? / What is the offer?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: All AKASH Subscribers will get BDT 12% (BDT 145.44) cashback on BDT 1,212.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q2. Where will the customer get this cashback?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Ans: Cashback will be instantly given to your Akash wallet. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q3. When I can avail this offer?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Ans: You can avail this offer by recharging BDT 1,212 to your Akash account in a single recharge from 01 December 2022 to 31 December 2022.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q4. When will I get the cashback?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Ans: Cashbacks will be given Instantly to your AKASH Wallet. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q5. Can I avail this offer more than once?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Ans: No. AKASH cashback will be available only once for a single AKASH Subscriber ID. </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q6. During campaign, if I recharge fractionally (not at a time) to make it BDT 1,212, will I get the cashback?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Ans: Fractional recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if you recharge BDT 600 and then BDT 612, you will not get the cashback. You need to recharge BDT 1,212 at a single recharge to get the cashback.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q7. What if I recharge more than BDT 1,212?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Ans: You can only avail this offer if your recharge amount is exactly BDT 1,212. You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than BDT 1,212.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q8. Will other offers be applicable for me if I avail this offer or vice versa?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of all other offers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">Q9: What is the conditions and benefit amount for Multi TV?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">A: 12% cashback for BDT 1,212 recharge in a single transaction.</span></span></p>\r\n', '1669804157-89871304.jpg', '1669804158-95182497.jpg', '1669804158-45204432.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 0, 1, '2022-11-30 23:55:14', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2022-11-30 16:29:18', '2022-11-30 16:29:18', 'Recharge', 9),
(145, 'Nagad Recharge Offer', 'Nagad-Recharge-Offer', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Any customers will get a total BDT 20 cashback on the exact monthly subscription fee (BDT 299/350/400) recharge through Nagad.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Campaign Duration:</strong> 10 December 2022 to 31 January<span style=\"color:black\"> 2023&nbsp;(53 days)</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>Terms &amp; Conditions:</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">All the customers of AKASH are eligible for this offer.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">BDT 20 Cashback will be given to the customer&rsquo;s Nagad wallet instantly after recharge.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer needs to recharge exactly the monthly subscription fee BDT 400, BDT 350, and BDT 299 to get the cashback.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Customer can avail this offer only once during the offer period.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Successive recharges will NOT be counted &amp; treated as a single recharge. For instance, if a subscriber recharges BDT 100 and then BDT 300, he will not get the cashback. Customer needs to recharge exactly the monthly subscription fee BDT 400, BDT 350, BDT 299 in a single recharge.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Offer can be availed only recharging from NAGAD App or NAGAD USSD. Customer will not be eligible for NAGAD Cashback if he/she makes payment through aggregator payment gateway or QR code scan.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">AKASH and Nagad reserves all rights to change, extend and cancel the offer at any 