xt-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q7. What if I recharge more than subscription fee?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: You will not get any cashback if you recharge more or less than subscription fee</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Q8. Will other offers be applicable for me if I avail this offer or vice versa?</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Ans: Yes, you can avail this offer on top of all other offers.</span></p>\r\n', '1670913612-12242810.jpg', '1670913613-33528390.jpg', '1670913613-60777943.jpg', 'Offer', 1, 0, 1, '2022-12-09 23:55:54', '2030-08-16 11:20:34', '2023-01-08 11:58:22', '2022-12-10 13:02:22', 'Recharge', 8),
